    1556,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/83512186019?pwd=BNyHZsomC0rkaqnAXBp4GXb262jtaj.1',
    '{"id":"01KFGG9HX162HBDYRDQP7PYWZW","title":"Tyfone // Marketers in Demand - Weekly Meeting (new)","summary":{"notes":"## **Content Production and Scheduling**\n\nThe team is maintaining a steady delivery of podcast episodes and video content while navigating tight schedules and upcoming travel commitments.\n\n- **Delivered 29 story points this month**, including the compilation video, with two episodes near completion for early February release, ensuring coverage through March 20th (09:04)  \n    - Episodes by Derek Aguilar and Costa will carry the schedule forward, supported by recordings of two additional episodes by Josh to fill any gaps.  \n    - Igor confirmed the backlog and schedule are sufficient to avoid major delays despite Josh’s heavy travel from February through May.  \n    - Josh plans accelerated episode turnarounds during travel, recording multiple episodes before leaving and immediately after returning.  \n    - Kevin and Jeremy remain the main quality gatekeepers for episode reviews, maintaining consistent production standards.\n\n- **High-quality speaking video content has been secured** using advanced filming gear and external audio setups to improve production value (04:09)  \n    - Josh explained security protocols delayed file transfers due to financial data restrictions but the process is resolved for future events.  \n    - Next speaking video scheduled for mid to late February, following the release of the long-awaited December footage next week.  \n    - Plans include dual camera setups and enhanced lighting to boost video quality for upcoming conferences.  \n    - Feedback will be requested promptly after delivery to incorporate improvements into future productions.\n\n## **Podcast Performance and Promotion**\n\nPodcast downloads spiked unexpectedly, prompting investigation and promotional strategy refinement to sustain and grow audience engagement.\n\n- **A notable spike of 122 downloads occurred on January 18th,** exceeding normal patterns and prompting review to identify causes (10:56)  \n    - Igor noted the spike does not align with recent episode releases, suggesting listeners may have returned to older content.  \n    - Josh requested Igor to notify Kevin for any recollection or insights on promotional activity that might explain the surge.  \n    - Baylee offered to arrange for Buzzsprout’s biweekly download notifications to better track episode performance and listener behavior.  \n    - Ongoing monitoring will help optimize timing and promotional tactics for maximum reach.\n\n- **Baylee introduced a podcast promotion checklist** to enhance audience interaction and discover growth opportunities (15:02)  \n    - Suggestions include adding regular, authentic calls for reviews to boost rankings and engagement.  \n    - Josh acknowledged the need to balance casual style with strategic asks to avoid alienating listeners.  \n    - Baylee will review recent episodes for additional promotional tactics used by other successful podcasts.  \n    - The team agreed to evaluate and possibly implement new engagement strategies to maximize impact.\n\n## **Competitive Positioning and Market Strategy**\n\nJosh shared an aggressive, creative response to a competitor’s podcast launch, emphasizing strategic domain acquisition and content differentiation to maintain market leadership.\n\n- **Josh and Kevin personally purchased all domain variations** of their main competitor Alchemy’s podcast name “Visionaries” to redirect traffic to their own podcast, creating a strategic edge (16:20)  \n    - This move counters competitor attempts to overshadow their brand and boosts their SEO presence.  \n    - Josh described the competitor as a publicly traded Goliath while positioning their company as the David gaining ground through consistent, high-quality content.  \n    - The competitor’s podcast features a high-profile industry speaker, likely costing several hundred thousand dollars annually, underscoring the competitive stakes.  \n    - Josh asked Baylee to review the competitor’s podcast and content for insights on further differentiation and ranking strategies.\n\n- **The competitive dynamic includes personal relationships and insider insights,** with the new SVP of sales formerly at Alchemy highlighting leadership frustration over being outpaced (21:15)  \n    - Alchemy now bookmarks Josh’s company’s news page, validating their rising influence in the digital banking space.  \n    - Josh emphasized the importance of staying ahead through consistency, quality, and creative tactics rather than reacting defensively.  \n    - Baylee committed to analyzing the competitor’s content and discussing strategic moves in the next meeting.  \n    - This story reflects a broader philosophy of proactive market positioning and leveraging brand authenticity.\n\n## **Long-Term Content Vision and Team Dynamics**\n\nThe team values the personal chemistry and authenticity that make their content resonate, aiming to capitalize on it for ongoing growth and audience connection.\n\n- **Josh highlighted the strong personal brand and chemistry between himself and senior solutions consultant Jimmy,** which enhances sales demos and content appeal (24:23)  \n    - Jimmy’s professional fitness influencer skills contribute to high-quality video content that elevates their production standards.  \n    - Their dynamic is seen as a key differentiator making presentations more engaging and relatable.  \n    - Josh expressed enthusiasm for continuing this style across future projects to maintain authenticity.  \n    - This approach supports the broader goal of content that feels genuine and builds lasting audience trust.\n\n- **Josh reflected on the podcast’s growth to 150 episodes,** crediting persistence and early support despite initial skepticism (24:55)  \n    - The podcast has become a major strategic asset, warranting continuous investment and refinement.  \n    - Josh is mindful of avoiding complacency and regularly seeks feedback to evolve the format and reach.  \n    - The team recognizes the importance of content as a competitive moat and a platform for thought leadership.  \n    - This long-term vision reinforces the need for ongoing innovation and responsiveness to audience and market shifts.","outline":null,"keywords":["Podcast production","conference speaking video","podcast analytics","competitor strategy","content backlog","travel schedule"],"overview":"- **Content Delivery:** Delivered 29 story points this month, ensuring content through March 20th with upcoming episode releases.  \n- **Video Quality Upgrade:** Advanced filming gear and dual camera setups enhance production for upcoming speaking videos scheduled for February.  \n- **Podcast Surge:** 122-download spike observed on January 18th; ongoing analysis to refine promotional strategies for sustained growth.  \n- **Competitor Strategy:** Acquired all domain variations of competitor''s podcast name to redirect traffic and strengthen SEO.  \n- **Proactive Positioning:** Emphasis on authenticity and consistency is crucial for maintaining market leadership and audience trust.  \n- **Podcast Growth:** Reached 150 episodes, recognized as a strategic asset; commitment to continuous improvement and audience engagement.","action_items":"\n**Baylee Gunnell**\nSend podcast promotion checklist to Josh DeTar and team to identify potential new strategies (15:02)\nInvestigate and enroll the team on Buzzsprout’s podcast episode notification system (12:00)\nReview competitor Alchemy’s podcast episodes and website to suggest new tactics for SEO and content quality improvements (20:05)\nReview and provide feedback on the upcoming conference speaking video footage to integrate improvements for next recordings (22:38)\n\n**Igor Zagradjanin**\nDeliver nearly completed podcast episodes by Monday or Tuesday for review and publishing (08:29)\nSend information on January 18–19 spike in podcast downloads to Kevin for further analysis (11:25)\n\n**Josh DeTar**\nCoordinate with Kevin to transmit the pending old conference speaking video next week (13:35)\nRecord two podcast episodes before departure to Maui and schedule backup episodes after return to maintain content pipeline through March (05:56)\n"},"duration":25.93000030517578,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"id":1,"name":"Josh DeTar"},{"id":2,"name":"Igor Zagradjanin"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Guys doing great.","index":0,"end_time":2.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":0.16,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Good.","index":1,"end_time":3.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3.2,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":2,"end_time":4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3.6,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Good to be back from.","index":3,"end_time":5.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":4,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":4,"end_time":5.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":5.36,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Holidays, little break.","index":5,"end_time":7.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":5.92,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"You''re doing fun.","index":6,"end_time":8.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":7.92,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, I gotta drive up the Pacific Coast.","index":7,"end_time":12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":9.44,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Oh, cool.","index":8,"end_time":13.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":12.4,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So, yeah, it was really pretty.","index":9,"end_time":14.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":13.28,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We went like, right after New Year''s and everything and I think everyone was back to work.","index":10,"end_time":20.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":15.04,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So, like, there was no traffic.","index":11,"end_time":22.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":20.92,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like, it was the perfect time to go.","index":12,"end_time":24.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":22.64,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Oh, that''s awesome.","index":13,"end_time":26.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":25.36,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, it was great.","index":14,"end_time":27.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":26.28,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Very cool.","index":15,"end_time":28.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":28.05,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Where''d you stay along the way?","index":16,"end_time":29.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":28.53,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"We just hit spots in California where we''ll definitely make it up to your neck of the woods next time.","index":17,"end_time":36.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":31.09,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But it''s a long drive.","index":18,"end_time":39.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":36.61,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s a really long drive.","index":19,"end_time":40.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":39.17,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So we started down in San Diego and then went up to the redwoods.","index":20,"end_time":46.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":41.41,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Oh, cool.","index":21,"end_time":47.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":46.45,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s awesome.","index":22,"end_time":48.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":47.17,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And you took Highway 1?","index":23,"end_time":49.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":48.61,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":24,"end_time":51.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":50.13,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"It is super pretty.","index":25,"end_time":53.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":51.81,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":26,"end_time":53.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":53.64,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"That''s neat.","index":27,"end_time":54.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":54.36,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Is that the first time you''ve done that?","index":28,"end_time":56.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":54.96,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":29,"end_time":57.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":57.08,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We gotta take our two dogs, too.","index":30,"end_time":60.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":57.56,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And that was like the best and the worst part of the trip.","index":31,"end_time":64.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":60.28,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like, so cute to see him at the beach, but man, like, planning a trip around, like, where is it dog friendly and stuff.","index":32,"end_time":72.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":64.4,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"That was hard.","index":33,"end_time":73.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":72.92,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, I bet.","index":34,"end_time":75.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":74.36,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":35,"end_time":76.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":75.72,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Nice.","index":36,"end_time":77.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":77.4,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"What about you, Igor?","index":37,"end_time":79.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":78.12,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, I took a week off actually.","index":38,"end_time":83.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":80.48,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Like.","index":39,"end_time":83.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":83.28,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, a bit more than a week.","index":40,"end_time":85.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":84,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah, it was.","index":41,"end_time":86.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":86.08,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"This was very good to take some rest and.","index":42,"end_time":88.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":86.8,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":43,"end_time":89.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":88.84,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Spend it.","index":44,"end_time":89.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":89.2,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Spend time with family.","index":45,"end_time":91.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":90.08,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"We.","index":46,"end_time":91.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":91.52,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"We are celebrating Christmas on January 7th.","index":47,"end_time":95.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":91.84,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Oh, yeah.","index":48,"end_time":96.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":96.08,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"We''re like two weeks after.","index":49,"end_time":98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":96.68,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":50,"end_time":98.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":98.24,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Nice.","index":51,"end_time":99.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":98.8,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"But it was.","index":52,"end_time":99.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":99.2,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"It was really nice.","index":53,"end_time":100.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":99.72,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yes.","index":54,"end_time":101.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":100.72,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Oh, that''s awesome.","index":55,"end_time":102.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":101.12,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":56,"end_time":103.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":103.6,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"How''s your holiday been?","index":57,"end_time":105.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":103.96,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"That was good.","index":58,"end_time":106.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":106.07,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"We.","index":59,"end_time":107.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":106.95,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"I took a little bit of time.","index":60,"end_time":109.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":108.15,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Not a ton, just kind of.","index":61,"end_time":111.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":109.55,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"We did a little bit of chill.","index":62,"end_time":112.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":111.19,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"We went out and went to Central Oregon and spent a couple of days out there.","index":63,"end_time":118.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":112.87,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"But we''re speaking at a conference in Maui next Saturday and then extend that out for two and a half weeks and stay out there.","index":64,"end_time":130.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":118.71,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So that''s going to be our.","index":65,"end_time":132.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":130.95,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, our big one for the year.","index":66,"end_time":134.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":132.66,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"I think that''ll be really fun.","index":67,"end_time":136.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":134.22,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":68,"end_time":137.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":136.9,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So.","index":69,"end_time":138.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":137.78,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, and speaking of that, we''ll get some more content out of that for you.","index":70,"end_time":142.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":138.58,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, we had some just crazy.","index":71,"end_time":145.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":142.98,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"I think you''ll understand why once you get the final product.","index":72,"end_time":148.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":145.46,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"I just got off the phone with Kevin.","index":73,"end_time":149.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":148.26,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"It''s actually his birthday this morning, so he''s.","index":74,"end_time":152.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":149.9,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Today.","index":75,"end_time":152.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":152.5,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So he''s.","index":76,"end_time":153.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":153.22,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"He''s out of the office today and he meant to get it over to you guys yesterday, but he just didn''t get it out.","index":77,"end_time":158.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":153.86,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So he''ll get it out to you guys next week.","index":78,"end_time":160.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":158.94,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"But we finally got all the video from the last conference.","index":79,"end_time":163.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":161.01,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"I spoke at but one of our senior solutions consultants does like full blown Instagram fitness influencer level shenanigans on the side.","index":80,"end_time":178.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":163.17,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Okay.","index":81,"end_time":179.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":178.53,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And he''s got all hardcore gear that he takes with him everywhere to video and do all of this.","index":82,"end_time":184.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":179.33,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So he used all of that, including external mic setups, whole nine yards for recording my speaking spot.","index":83,"end_time":192.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":184.85,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Oh, wow.","index":84,"end_time":192.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":192.18,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And we were just struggling with our freaking.","index":85,"end_time":195.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":192.86,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"I''ll give you a little bit of internal transparency.","index":86,"end_time":198.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":195.98,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Like because of what we do for work, this, we''re doing the right things.","index":87,"end_time":202.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":198.22,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"But because of what we do for work, and we house financial institution data and everything, our security protocols are like through the roof to the level where Jimmy''s laptop would not allow him to plug in a usb.","index":88,"end_time":214.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":202.94,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Oh my goodness.","index":89,"end_time":215.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":215,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So we couldn''t get it off of his external drives and everything.","index":90,"end_time":218.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":215.64,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So it was this whole rigmarole of having to work with it to allow that, to then allow a large enough file size download to move from him to Kevin to all of this.","index":91,"end_time":227.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":218.48,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Wow.","index":92,"end_time":228.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":227.96,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So it was just, it was this whole nightmare.","index":93,"end_time":230.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":228.6,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"But at least now we know how to do it for next time.","index":94,"end_time":232.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":230.44,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So we''ve got all of that stuff.","index":95,"end_time":234.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":233.4,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And then at this next conference, we''re going to do the same thing again.","index":96,"end_time":237.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":235,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So we''ll probably have two back to back speaking spots of video stuff for you guys to do the production on.","index":97,"end_time":246.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":238.04,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"But that stuff''s been really valuable, so.","index":98,"end_time":249.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":247.11,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":99,"end_time":249.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":249.07,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Oh, that''s awesome.","index":100,"end_time":250.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":249.43,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I''m excited to see this footage.","index":101,"end_time":252.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":250.27,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, it turned out really, really good.","index":102,"end_time":254.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":252.63,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"You got high quality audio.","index":103,"end_time":257.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":254.43,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And then for this next one, we''re going to take it even further and he''s going to do a dual camera setup and we''ll get both audience.","index":104,"end_time":263.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":257.51,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Oh, nice.","index":105,"end_time":264.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":263.43,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And then we''ll bring a little bit more lighting because the lighting wasn''t that great last time and.","index":106,"end_time":271.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":264.87,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And really try and make it look nice.","index":107,"end_time":273.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":271.84,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"You guys know the drill, right?","index":108,"end_time":274.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":273.32,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"I mean, yeah, we submit a speaking submission and somebody else does, and both speakers are equally as talented.","index":109,"end_time":279.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":274.28,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Both topics are as good, but one of them sends a higher quality production content.","index":110,"end_time":284,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":279.68,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"You''re going to get picked.","index":111,"end_time":285.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":284,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So, yeah, we just like to edge people out that way.","index":112,"end_time":287.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":285.04,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yep, 100%.","index":113,"end_time":289.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":287.76,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So we''ll do that.","index":114,"end_time":290.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":289.92,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":115,"end_time":292.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":291.68,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":116,"end_time":294.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":293.52,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"That''s super exciting.","index":117,"end_time":295.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":295.2,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Other than that word, kind of into the, the groove.","index":118,"end_time":301.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":295.76,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"I did want to say too, I really freaking loved that in the year video, how that turned out.","index":119,"end_time":306.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":301.32,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Thank you for working with me on that.","index":120,"end_time":309.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":307.32,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"That was like, I don''t want to say emotional, but like damn near emotional to like see that whole culmination of a year.","index":121,"end_time":316.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":309.32,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"It was pretty wild.","index":122,"end_time":317,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":316.08,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So I think that turned out cool.","index":123,"end_time":318.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":317.08,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"It''s crazy to think like how many people you talk to and.","index":124,"end_time":324.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":320.36,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, you think like 12 months ago you''re like crazy.","index":125,"end_time":330.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":324.57,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean I think this is now even outdated.","index":126,"end_time":336.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":331.85,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"But I did the math a little while ago and if you were to start at episode one and listen all the way through, I think now it takes like 10 days straight.","index":127,"end_time":345.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":336.25,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Oh, that''s awesome.","index":128,"end_time":349.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":346.25,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, like of 24 hour days.","index":129,"end_time":351.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":349.82,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Just 10 days straight.","index":130,"end_time":353.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":351.7,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Days.","index":131,"end_time":354.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":353.86,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":132,"end_time":354.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":354.22,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Non stop.","index":133,"end_time":355.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":354.74,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So yeah, we made a lot of content but yeah, that turned out really cool.","index":134,"end_time":360.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":356.02,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"We''re gonna start publicizing that heavily and then I think we''re going into a little bit of a stretch.","index":135,"end_time":369.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":361.14,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Bailey, I might, I might just give you a heads up of we might hit a couple of.","index":136,"end_time":374.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":369.7,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"I might have to have some accelerated turnaround times on some episodes to make sure we keep up because I''m into epic conference and travel season and I am.","index":137,"end_time":388.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":374.98,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, I am literally not home for more than three days in a row until May starting what, Saturday?","index":138,"end_time":397.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":388.38,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Oh my goodness.","index":139,"end_time":400.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":398.82,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, so I''m literally just trying to cram anytime I''m home.","index":140,"end_time":403.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":400.58,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"I''m trying to schedule an episode so keep as much.","index":141,"end_time":407.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":403.7,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And I''ve tried to build a backlog over the last little bit, but I had a couple of people have to move based on schedules and things.","index":142,"end_time":414.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":407.05,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So I''m recording two next week before we leave for Hawaii and then, and then right when I get back, I''m trying to schedule a couple to keep us up on top.","index":143,"end_time":427.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":415.25,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, so, but yeah, to make sure, just I wanted to give you a heads up there, there might be a couple where we might flirt with the.","index":144,"end_time":435.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":428.13,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"The two weeks a little bit.","index":145,"end_time":437.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":435.82,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, just.","index":146,"end_time":439.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":438.14,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, just shoot us a message whenever you need one.","index":147,"end_time":441.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":439.1,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"That''s needs to be done faster.","index":148,"end_time":443.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":441.82,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Well, I think Igor has like a couple updates to go over.","index":149,"end_time":449.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":445.42,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay.","index":150,"end_time":450.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":449.9,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yep.","index":151,"end_time":451.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":451.18,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So let''s quickly get into the genta.","index":152,"end_time":458.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":452.38,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Can you see the screen?","index":153,"end_time":462.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":461.07,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Cool.","index":154,"end_time":463.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":463.47,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So so far this month we have delivered 29 points including the compilation video.","index":155,"end_time":475.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":468.43,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"And I''m really glad you loved it.","index":156,"end_time":477.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":475.47,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"I really enjoyed working on it and yeah, it was, it was a journey and you can definitely see how it all came together so nicely.","index":157,"end_time":487.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":477.15,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"And then the episodes.","index":158,"end_time":490.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":489.04,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Derek Aguilar, I think, I''m not sure if you saw that.","index":159,"end_time":495.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":490.8,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"I think that Kevin responded to this.","index":160,"end_time":497.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":495.52,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So yeah, so we delivered this and also the next one, we''re really close to completing this.","index":161,"end_time":506.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":497.92,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So Monday or Tuesday you''ll have this.","index":162,"end_time":508.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":506.24,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Oh, okay, cool.","index":163,"end_time":510.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":509.85,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So yeah, so yeah, with these two, I think based on your bus sprout, I Think your schedule.","index":164,"end_time":518.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":512.25,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"I think that you''ll be covered for the February.","index":165,"end_time":521.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":518.61,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"I think.","index":166,"end_time":522.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":521.93,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So Derek takes us to the 6th of February.","index":167,"end_time":525.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":522.41,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":168,"end_time":526.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":526.49,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"And then Costa takes us to the 20th.","index":169,"end_time":529.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":526.93,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And then I will have recorded two in between that time period.","index":170,"end_time":536.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":530.25,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So that will take us to the 6th.","index":171,"end_time":540.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":537.77,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So that takes us to the 20th of March.","index":172,"end_time":543.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":541.53,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":173,"end_time":545.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":544.57,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"And I''ve got.","index":174,"end_time":545.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":545.13,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Okay, we should be good.","index":175,"end_time":548.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":547.53,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"We.","index":176,"end_time":549.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":548.85,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Actually, I don''t.","index":177,"end_time":550.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":549.09,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"I. I think we had one more in the hopper than I thought we did, Bailey.","index":178,"end_time":554.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":550.13,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So I think we may not flirt with it as much as I thought.","index":179,"end_time":557.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":554.89,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":180,"end_time":558.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":557.45,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Keep that in the back of my mind.","index":181,"end_time":559.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":558.33,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So I schedule.","index":182,"end_time":560.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":559.61,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"It''s fine.","index":183,"end_time":561.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":561.29,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"It''s fine.","index":184,"end_time":562.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":561.89,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Even if there are some tight deadlines, it''s.","index":185,"end_time":565.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":562.29,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"It''s gonna be okay.","index":186,"end_time":566.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":565.71,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"And then.","index":187,"end_time":568.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":567.91,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah, basically, we are waiting for your review of this episode.","index":188,"end_time":573.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":569.19,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"If you have any thoughts or if you just think it''s good to go, then.","index":189,"end_time":579.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":574.47,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ll leave that up to Kevin and Jeremy.","index":190,"end_time":582.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":579.83,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"That''s one of those.","index":191,"end_time":583.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":582.71,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"I haven''t looked at that stuff in so long.","index":192,"end_time":585.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":583.99,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Those guys really take care of me on that one.","index":193,"end_time":589.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":585.99,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So whatever they say, Igor goes.","index":194,"end_time":591.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":589.11,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Okay, cool, Cool.","index":195,"end_time":593.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":592.7,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Glad to hear that.","index":196,"end_time":595.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":594.14,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"And then your podcast stats.","index":197,"end_time":598.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":595.1,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":198,"end_time":600.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":599.66,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"The obvious spike on.","index":199,"end_time":603.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":601.66,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"What was that?","index":200,"end_time":604.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":603.58,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"This is like the.","index":201,"end_time":606.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":605.34,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Probably.","index":202,"end_time":606.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":606.38,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"This is January 18th, but I''m not sure why that was.","index":203,"end_time":616.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":607.34,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"January 18th.","index":204,"end_time":617.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":616.38,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":205,"end_time":618.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":618.14,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":206,"end_time":621.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":620.78,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So, yeah.","index":207,"end_time":624.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":622.94,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Sunday night.","index":208,"end_time":625.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":624.86,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":209,"end_time":628.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":627.34,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Sunday 18th and Monday, 19.","index":210,"end_time":629.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":628.02,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So there''s an obvious spike here.","index":211,"end_time":631.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":629.74,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Not sure why.","index":212,"end_time":632.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":631.9,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"I''m not sure when you.","index":213,"end_time":634.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":633.34,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"When you actually.","index":214,"end_time":637.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":634.42,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Here we go.","index":215,"end_time":638.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":637.34,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":216,"end_time":638.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":638.46,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Because it doesn''t make sense.","index":217,"end_time":639.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":638.82,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"The episode was published on January 9 and then the next one is in.","index":218,"end_time":645.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":639.98,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":219,"end_time":646.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":645.98,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So be that.","index":220,"end_time":648.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":646.7,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Be that as it may, it''s great that.","index":221,"end_time":650.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":648.62,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"I mean, yeah, we''ll take it, but.","index":222,"end_time":652.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":650.78,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":223,"end_time":652.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":652.46,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"That''s a lot of downloads.","index":224,"end_time":654.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":652.82,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"That is a lot.","index":225,"end_time":655.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":654.3,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"What the heck?","index":226,"end_time":656.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":655.98,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"I''m literally looking at my calendar trying to think of what happened.","index":227,"end_time":659.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":656.7,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Like, did I. Yeah.","index":228,"end_time":661.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":660.54,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"122 that day.","index":229,"end_time":665.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":661.5,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"That would have been before.","index":230,"end_time":666.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":665.82,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And who was that?","index":231,"end_time":669.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":668.54,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"What episode was it that they downloaded?","index":232,"end_time":671.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":669.74,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"We can look into that, but I''m not sure if Buzzsprout actually allows us to see which.","index":233,"end_time":680.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":673.78,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Which episodes are.","index":234,"end_time":682.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":680.74,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Were like, downloaded the most within that time period.","index":235,"end_time":685.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":682.26,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Igor, would you mind, like, just sending a note to Kevin too, on that, since he''s not on this meeting.","index":236,"end_time":691.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":685.22,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"I''d be curious if Kevin remembers if we did anything that.","index":237,"end_time":694.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":691.3,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Because that is a wild spike.","index":238,"end_time":697.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":695.7,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, for sure.","index":239,"end_time":699.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":698.43,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"For sure.","index":240,"end_time":700.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":700.27,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"I mean, it partly coincides with this.","index":241,"end_time":704.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":701.39,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Like.","index":242,"end_time":704.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":704.59,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So this episode got 122 downloads, so it may have pushed it a bit, but not like that.","index":243,"end_time":713.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":704.99,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Definitely.","index":244,"end_time":714.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":713.79,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":245,"end_time":714.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":714.31,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"It''s not enough for this large of a spike.","index":246,"end_time":717.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":714.55,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":247,"end_time":718.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":717.71,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Interesting.","index":248,"end_time":719.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":718.43,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, usually I find people go back to older episodes.","index":249,"end_time":724.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":720.91,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Do you get the notifications from Buzzsprout?","index":250,"end_time":727.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":724.89,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"They usually send one, like every other week.","index":251,"end_time":729.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":727.53,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Kevin might, but.","index":252,"end_time":732.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":731.13,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Okay, I can look into that if you want to get them.","index":253,"end_time":734.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":732.41,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So on the.","index":254,"end_time":736.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":735.37,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"For some reason, like on the website, it doesn''t show, but, like, they will send notifications like, hey, this last month you got from these episodes.","index":255,"end_time":746.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":737.13,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, I would love that.","index":256,"end_time":748.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":746.97,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And when I look at those, I''m like, oh, those are older episodes.","index":257,"end_time":751.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":748.17,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like, if you publish a new one, Like, a lot of them will come from that, but people go back to older episod too, so.","index":258,"end_time":757.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":751.61,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ll look into getting you added to those notifications then.","index":259,"end_time":762.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":757.35,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay.","index":260,"end_time":763.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":762.63,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, that''d be super cool.","index":261,"end_time":764.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":763.07,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Cool.","index":262,"end_time":767.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":767.35,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"And a question about the.","index":263,"end_time":772.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":768.15,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So the speaking video that you mentioned, I think, in December, and you then mentioned that you had some issues with the.","index":264,"end_time":781.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":772.55,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"With it finding the content or some technical issues, I can''t remember.","index":265,"end_time":787.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":782.16,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"But the speaking video that you mentioned you wanted us to do.","index":266,"end_time":791.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":787.6,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yep.","index":267,"end_time":792.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":792.32,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":268,"end_time":793.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":793.2,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So.","index":269,"end_time":793.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":793.64,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And then I would say, plan on probably seeing another one.","index":270,"end_time":797.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":793.92,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"In.","index":271,"end_time":800.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":800.16,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Mid to late February.","index":272,"end_time":803.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":802.72,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"We''ll get you that one.","index":273,"end_time":804.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":803.92,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"It''ll be the same style.","index":274,"end_time":808.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":807.76,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Okay.","index":275,"end_time":811.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":810.71,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So this.","index":276,"end_time":811.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":811.03,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So this is the one that you actually mentioned in December or.","index":277,"end_time":815.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":811.99,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah, this is.","index":278,"end_time":816.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":815.99,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"This is the old one that you''ve been waiting on for forever.","index":279,"end_time":819.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":816.75,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"We''ll get that one next week.","index":280,"end_time":820.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":819.07,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So when Kevin''s back on Tuesday, he''ll get you that one and then we''ll have a new one for you.","index":281,"end_time":826.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":820.87,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Probably end of February.","index":282,"end_time":828.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":826.35,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Okay.","index":283,"end_time":829.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":829.51,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Okay, sounds good.","index":284,"end_time":830.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":829.99,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah, I just wanted to.","index":285,"end_time":831.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":830.87,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"To be on the same page.","index":286,"end_time":834.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":831.91,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Cool.","index":287,"end_time":836.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":835.92,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So that''s it for, for the agenda.","index":288,"end_time":841.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":838.24,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Do we have anything else you want to ask, Mention, suggest?","index":289,"end_time":846.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":841.16,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"No, I can''t think of anything.","index":290,"end_time":851.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":849.84,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Like I said, I mean, Kevin and Jeremy do such a good job of taking care of the tactical stuff that I don''t really think about that.","index":291,"end_time":857.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":852.64,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"But I don''t know, I mean, from your guys''s perspective, I feel like we''ve hit such a long standing show now at this point.","index":292,"end_time":868.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":857.76,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Like, we''ve kind of got into a groove, but at the same time, I always want to be careful that we don''t just keep doing something because that''s the way we''ve always done it.","index":293,"end_time":876,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":868.48,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Like, are there any new things that we should be thinking about?","index":294,"end_time":879.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":876,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Different ways we should be approaching this?","index":295,"end_time":881.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":879.28,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Like, anything we''re doing wrong, Like, I mean, this has become a really, really, really big piece of our strategic, you know, content.","index":296,"end_time":892.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":881.6,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So, I mean, we we''re just doubling down on it more and more and more and using it more and more.","index":297,"end_time":898.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":893.92,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So we want to make sure we''re maximizing it.","index":298,"end_time":900.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":898.4,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":299,"end_time":902.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":902.48,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I recently put, together, like, a podcast promotion checklist of just the things I noticed that work really well.","index":300,"end_time":911.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":902.88,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I think you''re already doing a lot of the things on it, but I''ll shoot it over to you, and if there''s, like, anything on there you''re not doing, you can think about it.","index":301,"end_time":920,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":911.64,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And, like, maybe I''ll.","index":302,"end_time":922.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":921.34,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I''ll listen to some of your more, more recent episodes too, because there''s, like, some things I''ve noticed other podcasts do that are really helpful, like asking for reviews.","index":303,"end_time":933.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":922.58,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like, I''m not sure.","index":304,"end_time":936.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":934.62,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Is that something you''re doing right now?","index":305,"end_time":937.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":936.26,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So asking for reviews can help a lot.","index":306,"end_time":944.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":939.98,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like, and getting reviews, too, on your podcast boost your rankings a lot.","index":307,"end_time":949.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":944.3,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So, yeah, like, we could add something.","index":308,"end_time":952.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":949.63,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like, you know, if you.","index":309,"end_time":955.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":953.55,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"You have, like, your intro natural.","index":310,"end_time":957.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":955.63,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"That''s like, the same for every episode.","index":311,"end_time":959.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":957.47,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We could do the same.","index":312,"end_time":959.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":959.15,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Or you could just authentically ask for something different at the end of every episode if you wanted.","index":313,"end_time":965.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":959.95,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, actually, that''s a good can, I think, Bailey, I think we''ve even talked about this in the past.","index":314,"end_time":972.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":965.79,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Right?","index":315,"end_time":972.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":972.55,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Like, Kevin and I are super, super chill.","index":316,"end_time":975.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":972.87,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":317,"end_time":976.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":975.84,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We''re not petty until we are.","index":318,"end_time":978.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":976.72,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And then I''m really freaking petty.","index":319,"end_time":980.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":978.96,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":320,"end_time":981.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":980.72,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Did we tell you about the whole story of our.","index":321,"end_time":984.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":981.36,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Our largest competitor in our actual business started a podcast?","index":322,"end_time":988.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":984.56,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"No.","index":323,"end_time":989.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":988.96,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"No, I haven''t heard this.","index":324,"end_time":990.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":989.28,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Really?","index":325,"end_time":991.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":991.12,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"You have a minute?","index":326,"end_time":992.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":992,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"I''ll tell you.","index":327,"end_time":993.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":992.88,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, I love this story.","index":328,"end_time":995.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":993.52,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"It''s pretty fascinating.","index":329,"end_time":996.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":995.12,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So, you know, our podcast started, and of course they are.","index":330,"end_time":1001.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":996.8,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"In terms of even just our business, they''re significantly larger than we are.","index":331,"end_time":1004.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1001.57,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"They''re a publicly traded company.","index":332,"end_time":1006.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1004.65,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Right.","index":333,"end_time":1007.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1006.61,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And so they''re the David.","index":334,"end_time":1008.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1007.25,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Where the Goliath, or they''re the Goliath.","index":335,"end_time":1010.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1008.53,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"We''re the David in the story.","index":336,"end_time":1011.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1010.33,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Right.","index":337,"end_time":1012.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1011.65,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And we''ve just been kind of slowly chipping away at them.","index":338,"end_time":1015.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1012.93,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"We''ve been starting to piss them off a little bit more and more and more.","index":339,"end_time":1018.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1015.85,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"We''re starting to steal from them.","index":340,"end_time":1020.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1018.85,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"They''re not liking it.","index":341,"end_time":1021.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1020.25,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"We''re hitting their radar.","index":342,"end_time":1022.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1021.49,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And it was totally one of those things.","index":343,"end_time":1026.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1024.21,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"I guarantee you that if somebody had ever brought up our podcast, like, oh, that''s stupid thing that they''re doing, like, ha, good luck.","index":344,"end_time":1032.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1026.65,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And then all of a sudden, it kind of became a thing, and they were like, oh, crap.","index":345,"end_time":1036.109,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1032.749,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And so they went out and hired one of the biggest speaker names in our industry.","index":346,"end_time":1042.509,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1036.749,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"There''s kind of Two main guys, and they got one of them.","index":347,"end_time":1046.349,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1042.669,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And I wouldn''t be surprised if they''re paying this guy a couple hundred grand a year to do this podcast for them.","index":348,"end_time":1051.709,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1046.509,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And they got him to do this podcast for them.","index":349,"end_time":1055.469,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1052.509,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"They started it up, and they took direct shots at us, Bailey.","index":350,"end_time":1060.829,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1055.629,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Like, as soon as Kevin and I figured it out, we went and their site started saying things like, the best digital banking podcast and, like, some direct stuff.","index":351,"end_time":1071.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1060.98,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And Kevin and I were like, hey, we were gonna let you just, you know, we were gonna be cool with it, but now you''ve kind of pissed us off.","index":352,"end_time":1078.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1071.34,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And so we started doing a little bit of digging.","index":353,"end_time":1081.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1079.06,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"We started thinking about how we would target them in SEO, like, all of this stuff.","index":354,"end_time":1085.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1081.46,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Well, Kevin happens to figure out they named their podcast Visionaries.","index":355,"end_time":1090.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1085.14,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Like Visionaries, but fi.","index":356,"end_time":1093.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1091.05,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"For financial institution, like Visionaries.","index":357,"end_time":1095.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1093.05,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Right.","index":358,"end_time":1095.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1095.21,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So they use it everywhere.","index":359,"end_time":1097.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1096.17,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"It''s the name of their podcast.","index":360,"end_time":1098.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1097.33,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"If you go to the, you know, Spotify, it''s Visionaries.","index":361,"end_time":1102.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1098.65,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"You know what these idiots didn''t do?","index":362,"end_time":1103.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1102.17,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"They didn''t buy the domain.","index":363,"end_time":1104.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1103.65,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So Kevin and I bought it.","index":364,"end_time":1108.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1107.13,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yep.","index":365,"end_time":1109.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1109.37,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Kevin and I bought it personally.","index":366,"end_time":1112.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1110.33,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, Kevin and I bought every variation of it.","index":367,"end_time":1115.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1112.25,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So Kevin and I personally own every variation of their own domain.","index":368,"end_time":1121.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1116.44,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"If you go.","index":369,"end_time":1123,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1122.04,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And you go type in fissionaries.com, it takes you to our podcast.","index":370,"end_time":1127.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1123.24,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"We redirected the site, like, the whole nine yards.","index":371,"end_time":1131.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1128.76,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So that was our big screw you to them.","index":372,"end_time":1134.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1131.8,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"We definitely have been outranking them in different things.","index":373,"end_time":1139.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1136.6,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Like, we''ve been better at the consistency, all of this.","index":374,"end_time":1142.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1139.96,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"But where I''m going with all of this is I''d be really interested to get your take, if you wouldn''t mind taking a look at their podcast and all of that and just seeing if there''s other things that we can do that to make sure we continue to stay out ahead of these guys.","index":375,"end_time":1157.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1143.59,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So I''ll.","index":376,"end_time":1159.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1158.23,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Let me.","index":377,"end_time":1161.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1160.39,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"It''s actually.","index":378,"end_time":1163.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1163.35,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"See, it''s actually hard to find because.","index":379,"end_time":1172.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1168.32,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Kevin and I took their.","index":380,"end_time":1173.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1172.64,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Took everything.","index":381,"end_time":1174.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1174.16,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So, like.","index":382,"end_time":1175.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1175.04,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Is it Evergreen Podcast?","index":383,"end_time":1180.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1178.16,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"No, I think I might be on the wrong one.","index":384,"end_time":1183.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1181.92,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, here you go.","index":385,"end_time":1185.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1184.72,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Oh, yeah, that''s right.","index":386,"end_time":1188.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1186.8,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Because if you go to.","index":387,"end_time":1189.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1188.12,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So our competitor''s name is Alchemy.","index":388,"end_time":1192.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1190.56,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So if you go to Alchemy''s website and you go to their podcast, it''s alchemy.com digital banking podcast.","index":389,"end_time":1198.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1192.56,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And that was when Kevin saw that.","index":390,"end_time":1200.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1199.37,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"He was like, oh, screw you.","index":391,"end_time":1201.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1200.85,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"It''s on.","index":392,"end_time":1202.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1201.93,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, they started it.","index":393,"end_time":1204.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1202.49,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And so.","index":394,"end_time":1206.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1205.37,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So that''s where you can find it.","index":395,"end_time":1208.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1206.77,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So I just put that in the chat for you.","index":396,"end_time":1211.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1209.69,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"But, yeah, I Would love it if you could maybe just take a peek at that and see if there''s any other things that we can be doing just to make sure that even on the, like, Spotify''s and the YouTubes and stuff like that, that we outrank them, that we''re producing a better product.","index":397,"end_time":1225.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1212.17,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So, yeah, maybe take a look at, like, one of our last episodes.","index":398,"end_time":1228.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1225.69,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"One of their last episodes.","index":399,"end_time":1229.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1228.42,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"See what you think.","index":400,"end_time":1230.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1229.54,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, for sure.","index":401,"end_time":1231.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1230.42,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We''ll.","index":402,"end_time":1231.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1231.58,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We''ll check that out and we can chat through some ideas in our next meeting.","index":403,"end_time":1235.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1231.82,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like it?","index":404,"end_time":1237.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1236.42,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Thank you for sharing that story.","index":405,"end_time":1240.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1238.42,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"That is so crazy and awesome.","index":406,"end_time":1243.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1240.26,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":407,"end_time":1244.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1244.42,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"I mean, the best part was literally buying all the domains cost us like, I don''t know, a couple hundred bucks.","index":408,"end_time":1249.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1244.74,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And Kevin and I even made the joke.","index":409,"end_time":1251.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1249.54,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"We were like, I mean, this is absolutely something we would run through the corporate.","index":410,"end_time":1254.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1251.22,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"But we were like, we personally want to do this.","index":411,"end_time":1257.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1254.72,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":412,"end_time":1258.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1257.76,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"This has hit this level where we''re going to spend our own personal money and split it just as a screw you.","index":413,"end_time":1265.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1259.52,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yep, yep.","index":414,"end_time":1266.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1265.28,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I''m not petty until I am.","index":415,"end_time":1269.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1268.32,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And then.","index":416,"end_time":1270,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1269.64,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yep.","index":417,"end_time":1270.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1270,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"You know, they started it, so.","index":418,"end_time":1274.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1270.88,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, they deserved it.","index":419,"end_time":1275.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1274.16,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah, totally.","index":420,"end_time":1276.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1275.68,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":421,"end_time":1277.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1277.6,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Well, what''s funny is this.","index":422,"end_time":1279.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1277.96,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So there are.","index":423,"end_time":1280.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1279.2,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"We recently hired a new SVP of sales and.","index":424,"end_time":1287.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1281.26,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And the backstory that I''ve known him, we''ve been personal friends for like a decade, and he was at Alchemy for a while, so we had to be like, really good friends and direct competitors.","index":425,"end_time":1298.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1288.38,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So we''d go head to head during the week and then call each other on the weekend and see how we were doing, you know, And.","index":426,"end_time":1303.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1298.58,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And so it''s funny as Eric was like, it was really interesting the last days at Alchemy and, you know, him knowing he was coming over to us before they knew and hearing, like, how pissed off their senior leadership was getting at us for all that we were beating them.","index":427,"end_time":1319.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1304.3,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":428,"end_time":1319.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1319.42,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And everything.","index":429,"end_time":1320.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1319.78,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And he was.","index":430,"end_time":1321.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1320.86,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And one of the other things is our news and resources page.","index":431,"end_time":1324.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1321.5,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Apparently they used to talk a bunch of trash about it and thought it was the stupidest idea ever, and now they''re like, crap.","index":432,"end_time":1330.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1325.1,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Now we all have it bookmarked as where we go to get news is from our direct competitor.","index":433,"end_time":1334.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1330.46,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So we''re having a little bit of fun with them.","index":434,"end_time":1337.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1335.86,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"But, yeah, I''m always down for more.","index":435,"end_time":1339.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1337.42,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So.","index":436,"end_time":1339.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1339.06,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, if you see anything, think of anything, let me know.","index":437,"end_time":1341.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1339.3,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, we''ll.","index":438,"end_time":1343.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1342.02,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We''ll check that out.","index":439,"end_time":1344.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1343.1,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Cool.","index":440,"end_time":1344.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1344.26,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Love it.","index":441,"end_time":1345.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1344.7,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":442,"end_time":1346.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1345.7,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Other than that, that''s all I got.","index":443,"end_time":1348.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1346.58,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":444,"end_time":1349.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1348.5,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Well, always a pleasure.","index":445,"end_time":1350.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1349.22,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Great.","index":446,"end_time":1351.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1350.98,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Great to see you and excited for your Speaking videos.","index":447,"end_time":1355.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1351.34,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"That''s going to be.","index":448,"end_time":1356.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1355.98,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"To be in Maui.","index":449,"end_time":1358.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1356.9,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, totally.","index":450,"end_time":1359.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1358.42,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And actually, that''s another just what we''ll do.","index":451,"end_time":1363.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1359.22,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So I''ll make sure we get that over to you, like Tuesday when Kevin''s back.","index":452,"end_time":1367.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1363.42,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"If you could do me a huge favor and just do a quick cursory look over everything and give us any feedback.","index":453,"end_time":1373.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1367.34,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Because like I said, we''ll be shooting the next one the next week.","index":454,"end_time":1376.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1373.58,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So if there''s anything you want us to do different or that we could do better, just let us know because we can incorporate that into the next one.","index":455,"end_time":1382.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1376.86,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Oh, yeah, for sure.","index":456,"end_time":1383.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1382.86,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":457,"end_time":1384.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1383.9,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I''ll take a look at that footage then and see if there''s anything you can do better for the next one.","index":458,"end_time":1389.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1384.26,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"It sounds like you got a guy that really knows what he''s doing, though.","index":459,"end_time":1392.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1389.43,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Or maybe you said he does cars.","index":460,"end_time":1394.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1392.47,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"That might be.","index":461,"end_time":1395.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1394.79,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Just gonna keep you guys thoroughly entertained for the.","index":462,"end_time":1406.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1403.59,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"The week here.","index":463,"end_time":1409.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1408.39,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Let''s see.","index":464,"end_time":1412.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1411.51,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So this is our senior solutions consultant.","index":465,"end_time":1423.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1417.32,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And so he''s like our, you know, our demo guy and one of our personalities along.","index":466,"end_time":1429.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1424.84,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So Jimmy goes with me pretty much anytime there''s a big deal that we''re in.","index":467,"end_time":1433.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1429.72,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Like, we bring Jimmy and I, and I''m the executive that comes in and he''s the, like, you know, real technical expert and demo expert, and we just.","index":468,"end_time":1445.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1434.84,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"We''re kind of a.","index":469,"end_time":1446.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1445.73,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"A little bit of a larger than life pair together.","index":470,"end_time":1448.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1446.49,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"It''s pretty funny and it just works out.","index":471,"end_time":1450.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1448.33,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"But yeah, so that''s his.","index":472,"end_time":1452.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1450.37,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So he''s doing all of that on the side.","index":473,"end_time":1454.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1452.89,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And even when we travel for work, he brings all of his video gear and everything to film his workouts and stuff.","index":474,"end_time":1460.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1455.13,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And so then he just used all of that to shoot.","index":475,"end_time":1463.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1460.97,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And so he''s even upgraded all of his personal stuff since then.","index":476,"end_time":1466.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1463.29,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And we''re gonna.","index":477,"end_time":1467.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1467.33,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":478,"end_time":1468.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1467.97,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Anyway, yeah, Jimmy seems like a really cool guy.","index":479,"end_time":1471.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1468.29,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"He did that Penny AI video with you.","index":480,"end_time":1473.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1471.45,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, you.","index":481,"end_time":1474.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1473.97,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"You guys can have a fun banter, so.","index":482,"end_time":1476.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1474.61,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Oh, yeah.","index":483,"end_time":1477.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1476.69,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"I mean, that''s the same kind of thing.","index":484,"end_time":1478.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1477.25,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"It''s just.","index":485,"end_time":1478.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1478.49,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"That''s.","index":486,"end_time":1479.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1478.93,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"That''s fun when.","index":487,"end_time":1480.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1479.45,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"When work becomes not work and the people you work with are so much fun.","index":488,"end_time":1483.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1480.21,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And so.","index":489,"end_time":1484.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1483.65,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And people pick up on that, right.","index":490,"end_time":1486.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1484.77,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"In sales presentations, like.","index":491,"end_time":1487.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1486.09,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And that''s why Jimmy and I go together and do some of these and it works really well.","index":492,"end_time":1492.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1487.89,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s awesome.","index":493,"end_time":1494.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1493.06,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Cool.","index":494,"end_time":1496.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1495.86,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"All right, you guys.","index":495,"end_time":1497.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1496.3,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Well, I appreciate the time, as always, and.","index":496,"end_time":1499.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1497.02,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And all the stuff you guys do for us.","index":497,"end_time":1500.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1499.14,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"This is.","index":498,"end_time":1502.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1501.54,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"I think I even told this story when I was on a podcast recently about how our podcast started and I credit, you know, that Kevin and I were kind of talking about it.","index":499,"end_time":1512.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1502.34,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"They told Kevin, screw you.","index":500,"end_time":1513.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1512.7,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"I''m never doing that.","index":501,"end_time":1514.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1513.98,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And then the next day, Justin Cold emailed me and was like, we can help you do a B2B podcast.","index":502,"end_time":1519.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1515.06,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"I was like.","index":503,"end_time":1520.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1520.1,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"And here we are, like, years later and 150th episodes later and doing it.","index":504,"end_time":1526.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1521.14,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"So, yeah, crazy.","index":505,"end_time":1528.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1526.68,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":506,"end_time":1530.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1529.6,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":507,"end_time":1531.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1530.64,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Well, we''ll talk.","index":508,"end_time":1531.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1531.2,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Happy Friday, guys.","index":509,"end_time":1532.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1531.88,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Later.","index":510,"end_time":1533.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1533.12,"speaker_name":"Josh DeTar"},{"text":"Bye.","index":511,"end_time":1534.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1534.4,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Bye.","index":512,"end_time":1535.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1534.72,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"}],"dateString":"2026-01-23T16:30:00.000Z","host_email":"baylee.gunnell@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/83512186019?pwd=BNyHZsomC0rkaqnAXBp4GXb262jtaj.1","participants":["baylee.gunnell@marketersindemand.com,kevin.welsch@tyfone.com,josh.detar@tyfone.com,igor.zagradjanin@marketersindemand.com","kevin.welsch@tyfone.com","josh.detar@tyfone.com","igor.zagradjanin@marketersindemand.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01KFGG9HX162HBDYRDQP7PYWZW","organizer_email":"baylee.gunnell@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
    '{"label":"positive","confidence":0.92,"bullets":["Confirmed backlog of podcast episodes covers publishing through March 20; no scheduling gaps expected.","Resolved major tech blocker transferring video files by adjusting security protocols; streamlined future workflows.","Planned dual-camera setup and better lighting for upcoming Maui conference to improve content quality.","Team committed to faster episode turnarounds during travel season; Baylee offered support on short notice.","Baylee to analyze competitor podcast for ranking ideas; domain redirect tactics already helped outperform rival."],"highlights":[{"quote":"We redirected the site, like, the whole nine yards.","speaker":"Josh DeTar"},{"quote":"We''ll check that out and we can chat through some ideas in our next meeting.","speaker":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"quote":"We want to make sure we''re maximizing it.","speaker":"Josh DeTar"}],"topics":["delivery","content","workflow","rivalry"],"model":"openai/gpt-4","version":1,"generated_at":"2026-01-26T20:13:00Z"}'::jsonb,
