  '[{"text":"Send podcast promotion checklist to Josh DeTar and team to identify potential new strategies (15:02)","completed":false},{"text":"Investigate and enroll the team on Buzzsprout’s podcast episode notification system (12:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Review competitor Alchemy’s podcast episodes and website to suggest new tactics for SEO and content quality improvements (20:05)","completed":false},{"text":"Review and provide feedback on the upcoming conference speaking video footage to integrate improvements for next recordings (22:38)","completed":false},{"text":"Deliver nearly completed podcast episodes by Monday or Tuesday for review and publishing (08:29)","completed":false},{"text":"Send information on January 18–19 spike in podcast downloads to Kevin for further analysis (11:25)","completed":false},{"text":"Coordinate with Kevin to transmit the pending old conference speaking video next week (13:35)","completed":false},{"text":"Record two podcast episodes before departure to Maui and schedule backup episodes after return to maintain content pipeline through March (05:56)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
