''s just a separate landing page.","index":264,"end_time":1253.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1251.14,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Just a new page.","index":265,"end_time":1256.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1254.98,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right?","index":266,"end_time":1256.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1256.18,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"No pop up because.","index":267,"end_time":1257.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1256.5,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is that what you''re saying?","index":268,"end_time":1258.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1257.3,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like when they''re clicking join, we don''t want them to do the pop up?","index":269,"end_time":1260.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1258.1,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"No, because what happens when they do that because we use that Myco link is that they have to do they fill out their information one time and then into the microlink they fill it again a second time, which is kind of a bad user experience.","index":270,"end_time":1275.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1262.55,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We can''t avoid that though, because like, I mean, how do we avoid that?","index":271,"end_time":1279.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1276.31,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, we, we have to, we, we have to do that.","index":272,"end_time":1285.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1280.23,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s unavoidable because we need their, that lead information.","index":273,"end_time":1288.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1285.43,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Especially if there''s going to be a lot of abandoned cart leads.","index":274,"end_time":1292.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1289.9,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So the only question is, do you want it to be a popup or should it just be to a new page?","index":275,"end_time":1298.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1293.9,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"When they click join, we''re going to collect it no matter what.","index":276,"end_time":1303.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1299.34,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I''m just asking like design.","index":277,"end_time":1305.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1303.38,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I need to see what 2 new PA what to a new page would look like.","index":278,"end_time":1314.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1310.94,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"But I don''t think a pop up is a bad.","index":279,"end_time":1319.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1314.54,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s not a bad look, is it?","index":280,"end_time":1322.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1319.81,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Or it''s just like preference.","index":281,"end_time":1326.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1325.09,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Probably just depends on how much information we need from them.","index":282,"end_time":1333.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1329.97,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But that''s something we would need.","index":283,"end_time":1337.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1335.09,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Nina, it''s either a new page or a pop up.","index":284,"end_time":1340.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1337.57,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But we need it.","index":285,"end_time":1341.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1340.17,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"When they click on this is not the contact form, this is the, the membership page.","index":286,"end_time":1345.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1341.29,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"When they click on package A, they need to enter their lead information.","index":287,"end_time":1350.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1345.93,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We can give what.","index":288,"end_time":1356.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1353.85,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Sorry, does this have an.","index":289,"end_time":1359.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1357.93,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Like whichever way we go about this would.","index":290,"end_time":1362.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1359.45,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"If we were to find some kind of solution where like for example on the pop up they got their information and then it automatically put their information into the Myco link already.","index":291,"end_time":1373.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1362.17,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"What''s.","index":292,"end_time":1376.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1375.74,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Would that have an effect as to whether it''s better to do it as a pop up or on a new page?","index":293,"end_time":1382.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1376.22,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I think it won''t really matter.","index":294,"end_time":1385.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1383.82,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Like it''s just the user experience.","index":295,"end_time":1387.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1385.9,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay, Nina, is there a way where you think we could get the information from the form into the into the fields like pre fill it.","index":296,"end_time":1398.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1388.54,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Then on data track I would have.","index":297,"end_time":1402.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1398.91,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"To check because it''s usually like due to security protocols.","index":298,"end_time":1407.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1402.19,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Like it usually wouldn''t give you the option to refill with somebody else''s data.","index":299,"end_time":1412.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1407.35,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"How many people fill out website every month to like the membership page currently.","index":300,"end_time":1425.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1420.08,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Web?","index":301,"end_time":1429.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1428.64,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Well, based off of our lead sources.","index":302,"end_time":1432.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1429.2,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Not, not that many, not as many as we want.","index":303,"end_time":1435.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1432.32,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I believe last month was about 40 or 50.","index":304,"end_time":1438.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1435.84,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So but the thing is like it''s, I think it''s hard to go ahead.","index":305,"end_time":1447.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1442.24,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Well we, either way we, it sounds like we can''t like pre fill it so we just need to get that information across.","index":306,"end_time":1455.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1447.93,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So a link or something.","index":307,"end_time":1457.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1455.85,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Nina, like, do you want me to.","index":308,"end_time":1459.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1457.69,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like do a research on how we could maybe shorten the whole path with the microlinks and everything?","index":309,"end_time":1466.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1459.45,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So maybe there''s a way that we can get the lead information without them going to two separate lead forms.","index":310,"end_time":1473.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1466.17,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"How would that, how would that happen?","index":311,"end_time":1478.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1477.03,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Well, I can look into it and if we have some like realistic ways of solving it, maybe there''s a way that, you know, I mean there''s probably already something that can be plugged in so it doesn''t have to always show up twice.","index":312,"end_time":1494.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1479.99,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean I think that''s a good idea.","index":313,"end_time":1502,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1500.32,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"What do you think, eBay?","index":314,"end_time":1502.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1502,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":315,"end_time":1506.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1506.32,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But I mean don''t spend like five hours looking for something that might not exist.","index":316,"end_time":1510.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1506.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":317,"end_time":1512,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1511.6,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I, I, I just don''t know because what we need, what needs to happen is they, we need their information because they''re not going to complete the checkout.","index":318,"end_time":1523.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1515.6,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":319,"end_time":1524.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1523.84,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So either way, if this ends up being just another form somewhere, it''s still a form at the end of the day, it''s still a form.","index":320,"end_time":1529.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1524.67,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We still got to get it somehow.","index":321,"end_time":1531.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1529.95,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We''re not going to get the emails of people who visit the site.","index":322,"end_time":1534.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1531.63,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They have to give it to us willingly.","index":323,"end_time":1536.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1534.15,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So I don''t know how there could be a way where we could save that information.","index":324,"end_time":1543.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1538.91,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You know, as they''re going through the process.","index":325,"end_time":1548.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1546.59,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It used to be like, I mean.","index":326,"end_time":1550.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1548.67,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"There are pages like it.","index":327,"end_time":1552.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1550.68,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I mean you probably notice also when you''re like shopping online and then you don''t really finish a purchase but you get an email and you don''t like it doesn''t lead you to two separate forms to do that.","index":328,"end_time":1563.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1552.08,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s like an abandoned cart lead.","index":329,"end_time":1566.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1564.36,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We used to work with a company.","index":330,"end_time":1568.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1567.16,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Isn''t that ABC feature?","index":331,"end_time":1571.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1570.6,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t know if it''s an ABC feature.","index":332,"end_time":1575.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1573,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It may, I know that we used to work with a company that, that did that.","index":333,"end_time":1579.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1575.96,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So Any abandoned cart lead would come through.","index":334,"end_time":1583,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1579.96,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Is it sweaty?","index":335,"end_time":1584.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1583.24,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Sweaty, Exactly.","index":336,"end_time":1585.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1584.6,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s.","index":337,"end_time":1586.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1585.88,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s the same.","index":338,"end_time":1586.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1586.28,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s the same thing, though.","index":339,"end_time":1588.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1586.92,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s actually the same thing.","index":340,"end_time":1589.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1588.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Remember, when they click into the thing, they have to give us information.","index":341,"end_time":1594.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1589.64,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right?","index":342,"end_time":1596.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1596.04,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So, Nina, like in that example, how would they know to email you?","index":343,"end_time":1599,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1596.36,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"At some point you had to put your email on something.","index":344,"end_time":1601.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1599.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":345,"end_time":1602.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1601.6,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So you had.","index":346,"end_time":1602.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1602.32,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So that''s the thing is we don''t.","index":347,"end_time":1605.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1602.84,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"There is no way to get that unless it''s currently the checkout page.","index":348,"end_time":1610.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1606.25,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And you guys can''t edit because that''s a different software.","index":349,"end_time":1612.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1610.49,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And not only that, that software needs to take that field and dump it into HubSpot even when it''s not submitted.","index":350,"end_time":1619.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1613.37,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So maybe it''s an ABC question.","index":351,"end_time":1625.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1621.45,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And I, and I think the answer is no because we asked for that like a year ago.","index":352,"end_time":1629.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1626.65,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Hey, you know, if they''re filling out your form, your checkout page on the first section, if they put the email down, can we somehow, like, it only works if you use our CRM, something like that, like not HubSpot.","index":353,"end_time":1641.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1629.69,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":354,"end_time":1644.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1643.62,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So I just don''t want you, Nina, to look, investigate and realize like this is.","index":355,"end_time":1650.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1645.46,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You''re investigating us.","index":356,"end_time":1651.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1650.14,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You''re going to data track the software and realize like, that''s just a question.","index":357,"end_time":1657.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1651.3,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We should just ask them.","index":358,"end_time":1658.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1657.42,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Milan, do you want.","index":359,"end_time":1662.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1661.71,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, let me.","index":360,"end_time":1663.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1662.75,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I''ll ask Amanda.","index":361,"end_time":1664.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1663.95,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Just.","index":362,"end_time":1665.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1665.23,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Just ask her like, because I think, I think we already asked her and she''s like, no, no, not.","index":363,"end_time":1670.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1665.63,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Not really a way to do that using HubSpot.","index":364,"end_time":1672.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1670.55,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And you can tell her we use HubSpot for CRM.","index":365,"end_time":1674.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1672.31,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You guys.","index":366,"end_time":1676.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1676.43,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I know Colin said you guys have framework developers, so if we gave you access to it, could you just like, once we''re at that stage, can you just build the connection points?","index":367,"end_time":1685.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1676.91,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s not been into it.","index":368,"end_time":1688.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1686.16,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"What, what it costs us money for each time we give editor access.","index":369,"end_time":1693.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1688.72,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is there an email that you guys could share?","index":370,"end_time":1696.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1693.68,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I will ask them and I will forward it.","index":371,"end_time":1700.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1697.92,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Forward it.","index":372,"end_time":1700.759,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1700.24,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And just we can get on Slack.","index":373,"end_time":1702.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1700.759,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And then just looking ahead, though, we''re gonna mostly at the website, it''s mostly text and videos and that kind of thing, but we do want analytics and we do want whatever pixels you think is relevant.","index":374,"end_time":1720.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1704.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Important to kind of make sure the SEO is there and make sure the tracking is there so we know what people are coming in.","index":375,"end_time":1728.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1720.86,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So anything that''s not related to the design is free game for you all to like spend a little bit of time just getting it ready.","index":376,"end_time":1736.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1728.7,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So.","index":377,"end_time":1737.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1737.38,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So put that in your list of to dos and then send me the email that we should give access to and then I can, I can just make you all access now and then you can do this in parallel while we''re putting in images and words, you can in parallel start to do everything else you need.","index":378,"end_time":1755.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1738.02,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Okay.","index":379,"end_time":1757.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1756.38,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay.","index":380,"end_time":1760.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1760.22,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I just, I just reached out to abc so hopefully I get my answer fairly soon.","index":381,"end_time":1765.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1760.62,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And like, I don''t know if we''re going to get into this, but you guys have started running ads.","index":382,"end_time":1770.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1765.98,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Milan, like can we spend a little bit of time just on like, like what are we looking at?","index":383,"end_time":1776.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1771.13,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like open up at what are we looking at next couple weeks?","index":384,"end_time":1779.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1776.81,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, absolutely.","index":385,"end_time":1782.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1781.53,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Nina, are you, are you running ads or someone else doing it for us?","index":386,"end_time":1787.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1783.13,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We had, we have a paid media specialist.","index":387,"end_time":1789.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1787.33,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay.","index":388,"end_time":1790.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1790.33,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And is that person.","index":389,"end_time":1791.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1790.85,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And normally like that person can''t join our team, join these calls.","index":390,"end_time":1796.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1792.25,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They usually don''t do meetings because they have a lot like they, we have hours where they have to do specific maintenance tasks and everything.","index":391,"end_time":1804.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1796.82,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So they don''t really spend time time on minute meetings.","index":392,"end_time":1807.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1804.18,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay.","index":393,"end_time":1808.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1807.46,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But any question you have I can forward and they will answer it''s not problem.","index":394,"end_time":1813.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1809.54,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay.","index":395,"end_time":1817.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1817.38,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So that.","index":396,"end_time":1818.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1817.82,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Can you guys see my screen?","index":397,"end_time":1819.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1818.42,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":398,"end_time":1820.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1819.78,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":399,"end_time":1821.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1821.3,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So this is what we''ve currently God active ebay.","index":400,"end_time":1824.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1821.74,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So we have two dollar down campaigns and then two trial experience campaigns.","index":401,"end_time":1830.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1824.85,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Nina, I got an email today saying that the trial, I think it was the trial experience campaigns were approved by Meta.","index":402,"end_time":1838.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1832.01,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It looks like if they''re learning they haven''t been approved yet.","index":403,"end_time":1844.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1839.61,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Right.","index":404,"end_time":1845.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1844.81,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Or they have now they''re in the learning phase.","index":405,"end_time":1847.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1845.29,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Like if they''re approved it means there''s nothing like suspicious surrounding the content.","index":406,"end_time":1854.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1848.81,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Like there''s no like words that shouldn''t be used or you know, clickbait wording or anything like that.","index":407,"end_time":1860.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1854.2,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Learning means that the algorithm is still learning how to behave.","index":408,"end_time":1865.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1860.8,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So it means just that we shouldn''t like change anything in this time that while it''s learning.","index":409,"end_time":1869.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1865.08,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So there''s Miami trial.","index":410,"end_time":1871.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1869.56,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I understand.","index":411,"end_time":1872.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1871.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So there''s two trials for each club and then the dollar enrollment.","index":412,"end_time":1875.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1872.36,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":413,"end_time":1876.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1875.72,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Which are they all.","index":414,"end_time":1877.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1876.28,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Are they all through that?","index":415,"end_time":1878.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1877.48,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is there a cost per lead or some of them impressions or do you know what I mean?","index":416,"end_time":1883.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1878.68,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like.","index":417,"end_time":1884.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1883.82,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Oh, it looks like.","index":418,"end_time":1885.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1884.34,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Go ahead.","index":419,"end_time":1888.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1888.34,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"They all have lead forms.","index":420,"end_time":1890.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1889.14,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Like two are, you know, the microlinks and the two other ones are the non index pages.","index":421,"end_time":1896.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1891.06,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"What''s the cost per lead now can you squeak scroll and off cost per result.","index":422,"end_time":1902.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1897.3,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That.","index":423,"end_time":1903.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1903.22,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So how does that make sense?","index":424,"end_time":1904.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1903.7,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"How is it 60 cents?","index":425,"end_time":1906.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1904.78,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because it''s only.","index":426,"end_time":1908.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1908.27,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"It started from Monday.","index":427,"end_time":1911.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1909.87,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So if there''s not a lot of data.","index":428,"end_time":1913.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1912.19,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"It doesn''t.","index":429,"end_time":1915.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1915.07,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"These aren''t leads though, right?","index":430,"end_time":1917.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1915.87,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"These are just landing page views.","index":431,"end_time":1918.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1917.15,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":432,"end_time":1919.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1919.31,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"These are like impressions, something like that.","index":433,"end_time":1922.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1919.71,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So they''re not forms.","index":434,"end_time":1924.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1922.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They''re not submitting forms.","index":435,"end_time":1925.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1924.35,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"These two campaigns, you''re just capturing them to go to a website?","index":436,"end_time":1932.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1928.51,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"No.","index":437,"end_time":1935.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1935.36,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So these two campaigns are leading people to lead forms.","index":438,"end_time":1939.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1935.6,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So if they fill it, we will have a lead, but if they don''t fill it, we don''t get their information.","index":439,"end_time":1947.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1940.72,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"How do we see how many people have filled out the form?","index":440,"end_time":1949.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1947.2,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"When they fill out the form, where.","index":441,"end_time":1952.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1950.4,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Is it showing here?","index":442,"end_time":1953.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1952.68,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Does it.","index":443,"end_time":1954.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1953.6,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Doesn''t it show how many people fill out the form?","index":444,"end_time":1956.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1954.04,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I saw it.","index":445,"end_time":1957.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1956.88,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I saw it here the other day and I don''t know where it''s gone.","index":446,"end_time":1960.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1957.68,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Blank clicks.","index":447,"end_time":1964.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1963.83,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"There, there''s.","index":448,"end_time":1965.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1964.71,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Nina.","index":449,"end_time":1965.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1965.55,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Normally there''s like.","index":450,"end_time":1966.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1965.95,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"You should have, like.","index":451,"end_time":1967.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1966.71,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":452,"end_time":1970.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1968.55,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I can''t see it for some reason.","index":453,"end_time":1971.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1970.03,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"See, I. I literally yesterday I wa