ing about on here?","index":498,"end_time":2223.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2222.18,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"No, Google it.","index":499,"end_time":2225.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2224.82,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t remember the URL.","index":500,"end_time":2227.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2225.9,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Okay, okay.","index":501,"end_time":2228.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2227.46,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Paid ads.","index":502,"end_time":2231.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2230.1,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Meta dev.","index":503,"end_time":2232.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2231.22,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I.","index":504,"end_time":2248.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2248.19,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Keep scrolling.","index":505,"end_time":2249.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2248.39,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Go back to Google.","index":506,"end_time":2256.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2255.71,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Keep scrolling.","index":507,"end_time":2259.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2258.35,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"There''s a way to test it on.","index":508,"end_time":2276.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2275.16,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"On the actual campaign and ad set.","index":509,"end_time":2279,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2277.08,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"No.","index":510,"end_time":2279.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2279,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I mean there should be.","index":511,"end_time":2284.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2283.16,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"But also I wouldn''t expect like leads coming in direct directly from two campaigns that are still in learning phase.","index":512,"end_time":2289.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2284.16,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Well, one of them is not in learning phase.","index":513,"end_time":2292.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2291.08,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Any.","index":514,"end_time":2293.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2292.76,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I think I might have found it.","index":515,"end_time":2309.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2308.05,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s Hesley.","index":516,"end_time":2316.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2314.05,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It is.","index":517,"end_time":2318.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2318.05,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"The website.","index":518,"end_time":2321.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2321.26,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":519,"end_time":2324.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2323.66,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So these are active, you know, they''re not in learning base.","index":520,"end_time":2332.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2326.22,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I mean they''re all active, but you always have a certain point where the algorithm started working and it''s starting to show it to people, but like it still needs to, you know, grow attention.","index":521,"end_time":2344.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2332.22,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay, when, when should, for example, if.","index":522,"end_time":2349.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2347.19,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"You click on the $1 down campaign.","index":523,"end_time":2354.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2349.47,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, I just dropped the link in chat.","index":524,"end_time":2360.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2358.31,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"In the zoom chat.","index":525,"end_time":2361.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2360.39,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, I understand.","index":526,"end_time":2367.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2365.83,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"You mean that.","index":527,"end_time":2367.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2367.03,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"What, so when do you think we''re going to start seeing leads?","index":528,"end_time":2370.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2367.71,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Well, I would expect it like I would leave this this week to, for it to learn.","index":529,"end_time":2377.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2372.96,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And then on next week if we don''t see any changes, we can see if something needs to be optimized.","index":530,"end_time":2382.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2377.48,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Click on.","index":531,"end_time":2385.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2385.04,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Go to.","index":532,"end_time":2386.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2386.4,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Click on page.","index":533,"end_time":2387.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2386.88,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You have to go to this one.","index":534,"end_time":2389.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2388.48,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":535,"end_time":2391.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2390.64,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Product.","index":536,"end_time":2391.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2391.36,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"This looks a little different than I''m.","index":537,"end_time":2394.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2392.64,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What I''m used to.","index":538,"end_time":2395.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2394.4,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I remember it looking like this.","index":539,"end_time":2397.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2395.92,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Which form?","index":540,"end_time":2400.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2399.98,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is there a specific form that we''re using?","index":541,"end_time":2403.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2400.54,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What is that, Nina?","index":542,"end_time":2407.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2405.02,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Which form do we use?","index":543,"end_time":2408.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2407.66,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We use two forms for the trial campaign.","index":544,"end_time":2412.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2409.5,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"One is for Florida, the other one for Miami and then we use two microlinks for the dollar down campaign.","index":545,"end_time":2419.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2412.78,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So which one is it?","index":546,"end_time":2421.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2420.06,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Here.","index":547,"end_time":2421.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2421.14,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Just a second.","index":548,"end_time":2428.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2427.87,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I think that here you can only see the HubSpot forms.","index":549,"end_time":2487.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2485.01,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I don''t know if you can see the forms that are external only.","index":550,"end_time":2493.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2487.85,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Only this one.","index":551,"end_time":2494.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2493.17,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":552,"end_time":2495.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2494.53,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":553,"end_time":2497.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2497.01,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So, so my, my, if we, if they don''t fill out this form, then do we not capture the, the results?","index":554,"end_time":2509.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2497.41,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Well, you need to have like a lead has to become a lead for it to be trapped.","index":555,"end_time":2518.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2512.54,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I guess, I guess another way to say is like, I think I understood meta to, to be like, if you do impressions, you can''t really track cost.","index":556,"end_time":2530.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2520.22,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"The cost per result is based.","index":557,"end_time":2532.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2530.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is not based on form submission, it''s based on.","index":558,"end_time":2536.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2532.67,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yes, but this is not a brand awareness campaign.","index":559,"end_time":2540.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2536.11,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So for example, if they fill in, they have a form and when they fill it in, we see it in HubSpot as paid social.","index":560,"end_time":2547.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2540.67,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"But I know you''re seeing a HubSpot, but I want to see it here, which tells us the cost per result, right?","index":561,"end_time":2553.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2547.87,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because HubSpot doesn''t tell us the cost per result, meta does.","index":562,"end_time":2556.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2553.35,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So if you set it up to say, hey, it''s dumping a HubSpot, that''s fine.","index":563,"end_time":2560.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2557.18,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That''s how it should work.","index":564,"end_time":2561.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2560.78,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But you''re also having them direct to a HubSpot form, not a metaphor.","index":565,"end_time":2566.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2562.14,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You don''t direct them to a meta form.","index":566,"end_time":2567.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2566.3,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"The conversion is landing page views.","index":567,"end_time":2571.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2568.78,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s not form submissions.","index":568,"end_time":2573.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2571.58,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So before you guys started, we were using meta forms and then metaforms is connected to HubSpot.","index":569,"end_time":2581.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2574.46,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So.","index":570,"end_time":2582.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2581.9,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So everything does work.","index":571,"end_time":2583.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2582.06,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It does sink into HubSpot.","index":572,"end_time":2584.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2583.1,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s just on the front end.","index":573,"end_time":2586.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2585.5,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"If you don''t use the metaphor, then we can''t see the cost per lead.","index":574,"end_time":2592.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2586.94,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We would have to take all the money that we spend that month, divide by the number of paid ads in HubSpot.","index":575,"end_time":2600.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2593.66,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We have to manually do the math.","index":576,"end_time":2601.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2600.1,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And we were not going to, you know, you know what I mean?","index":577,"end_time":2604.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2601.3,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because in the past when we ran this look like you can see lead form, right?","index":578,"end_time":2608.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2605.02,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"The ad is set up as a lead form versus a landing page view because you put the conversion as a landing page as going to another place.","index":579,"end_time":2620.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2609.35,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"HubSpot.","index":580,"end_time":2621.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2620.47,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think we can''t use that.","index":581,"end_time":2623.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2621.99,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We have to use the metaphor.","index":582,"end_time":2626.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2625.11,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So do you want us to change the campaigns into metaphor?","index":583,"end_time":2630.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2627.19,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I think they have to be talk to your person because then you have.","index":584,"end_time":2634.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2630.95,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Or the trial campaign, then it loses the purpose of getting people to add more information to the form.","index":585,"end_time":2641.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2635.49,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Why don''t we.","index":586,"end_time":2643.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2642.53,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We updated the trial campaign forms so that we could get more qualified leads.","index":587,"end_time":2653.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2646.37,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So we asking them like more qualifying questions.","index":588,"end_time":2656.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2653.45,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We can have different forms in meta.","index":589,"end_time":2660.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2658.05,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We can create a trial Florida form.","index":590,"end_time":2662.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2660.01,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We can create a Miami regular form.","index":591,"end_time":2665.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2662.82,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We can create forms in meta.","index":592,"end_time":2667.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2665.58,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":593,"end_time":2668.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2667.98,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Sorry.","index":594,"end_time":2669.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2669.5,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"This baby''s like trying to talk at me.","index":595,"end_time":2673.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2670.54,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"He''s telling me I''m.","index":596,"end_time":2675.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2674.38,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I''m wrong.","index":597,"end_time":2676.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2675.62,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":598,"end_time":2679.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2679.26,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I mean it depends like what''s the priority.","index":599,"end_time":2686.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2682.46,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So for example, for the HubSpot forms that we have now for the trial experience, you have certain prop properties within HubSpot that will give you.","index":600,"end_time":2695.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2686.3,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"For example, if a salesperson wants to see leads that are more interested than others, they will get more information from the lead form.","index":601,"end_time":2703.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2695.46,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"But I don''t know how much does the meta form other than just join us and put some specific information.","index":602,"end_time":2709.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2703.94,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"It usually has, you know, a limit to how creative you can be with the questions.","index":603,"end_time":2716.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2709.3,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"You can only ask.","index":604,"end_time":2717.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2716.66,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"You look at, look at the form because I think it''s any other form.","index":605,"end_time":2721.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2718.34,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like you''re only asking people what text, text questions, multiple choice drop downs.","index":606,"end_time":2728.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2721.69,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s the same stuff, right?","index":607,"end_time":2729.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2728.29,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s the same thing.","index":608,"end_time":2730.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2729.93,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So I think we need to get this switched over as soon as.","index":609,"end_time":2734.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2731.45,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Can we do a mixture?","index":610,"end_time":2735.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2734.69,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Can we do a mixture?","index":611,"end_time":2737.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2735.93,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"You can do whatever It''s a metaphor, it''s a meta.","index":612,"end_time":2739.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2737.05,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s just a form.","index":613,"end_time":2740.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2739.69,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s a form builder.","index":614,"end_time":2741.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2740.41,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":615,"end_time":2741.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2741.53,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"When you create meta, you say what question do you want?","index":616,"end_time":2743.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2741.81,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You''re creating.","index":617,"end_time":2744.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2743.73,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You''re literally creating forms.","index":618,"end_time":2745.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2744.21,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But I think my point is that you can create the same form in meta.","index":619,"end_time":2751.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2746.09,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"If you don''t create it in meta, then we are not going to see on this table cost per result for form conversion.","index":620,"end_time":2760.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2751.17,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We''ll see cost per result for how many people go to the page, but it''ll be harder for us to track the true conversion.","index":621,"end_time":2767.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2760.01,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like how efficient are we at using at our ad spend?","index":622,"end_time":2770.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2767.33,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because.","index":623,"end_time":2772.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2772.29,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because to then know that we have to go to HubSpot and manually figure out the math.","index":624,"end_time":2778,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2773.01,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"How many leads do we get from HubSpot for campaign?","index":625,"end_time":2781.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2778.32,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"1 divided by how much money did we spend vs here prints it nicely in a tape.","index":626,"end_time":2786.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2781.28,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":627,"end_time":2786.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2786.48,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Here I think you''ve probably seen cost per result, but then again it could be difficult to interpret it.","index":628,"end_time":2792.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2786.92,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"It''s cost per.","index":629,"end_time":2793.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2792.88,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s.","index":630,"end_time":2794.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2793.68,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s always labeled cost per result.","index":631,"end_time":2795.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2794.04,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But the, if you look at the result column it means it''s different things.","index":632,"end_time":2800.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2795.68,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right?","index":633,"end_time":2800.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2800.24,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Landing page views and forms, we should just keep it forms.","index":634,"end_time":2805.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2800.72,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It should always be that same type.","index":635,"end_time":2806.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2805.45,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And we might run some landing page views like just to build awareness perhaps like on our website.","index":636,"end_time":2812.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2807.25,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You know, we could do a little bit of that, but it''d be really hard for us to go back like at the end of the month and say how much did we spend?","index":637,"end_time":2819.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2812.45,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What campaign was most successful?","index":638,"end_time":2820.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2819.21,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"How much?","index":639,"end_time":2821.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2821.17,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Well, it''s not even how much money we spent, it''s how much dollars did it cost for someone to fill out that form.","index":640,"end_time":2828.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2821.73,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Okay.","index":641,"end_time":2830.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2829.66,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And Meta and HubSpot isn''t going to give us that like cleanly.","index":642,"end_time":2833.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2830.54,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":643,"end_time":2835.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2834.86,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So because this is linked to meta billing, so I think you may have to build it into this form and then just make sure as long as they''re integrated should be fine.","index":644,"end_time":2843.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2835.18,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because that''s what we have been doing like last.","index":645,"end_time":2845.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2843.06,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Okay, it''s the same, it''s what we had been doing and just keep the forms clean.","index":646,"end_time":2851.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2845.66,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You know, delete old forms that we don''t use.","index":647,"end_time":2853.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2851.66,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like keep the forms really like while labeled so we know what forms goes to what and it really should lead to the same place.","index":648,"end_time":2862.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2853.62,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But what we can see now today is that no leads have come through.","index":649,"end_time":2866.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2863.32,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Mostly like we haven''t gotten any leads.","index":650,"end_time":2869.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2867.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":651,"end_time":2869.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2869.28,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s not showing up.","index":652,"end_time":2871,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2870.04,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Spot is not here.","index":653,"end_time":2871.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2871.079,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We just haven''t got.","index":654,"end_time":2872.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2871.96,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So we should be seeing leads like very soon here.","index":655,"end_time":2876.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2872.84,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s a bit concerning why there''s nothing, even if it''s taking a little bit of time.","index":656,"end_time":2882.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2876.84,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You know, which pages are they being sent to?","index":657,"end_time":2887.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2884.89,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Which landing page are they being sent to?","index":658,"end_time":2890.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2888.17,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So the trial campaign is sent to the two non index pages.","index":659,"end_time":2895.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2890.81,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"That starts to build with the lead gen forms with the questions and the other two are the microlinks.","index":660,"end_time":2902.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2895.81,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"What are the mic.","index":661,"end_time":2905.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2904.49,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What are microlinks?","index":662,"end_time":2906.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2905.33,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That''s.","index":663,"end_time":2907.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2906.85,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, so that''s why we''re not collecting lead information.","index":664,"end_time":2909.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2907.17,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Right.","index":665,"end_time":2912.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2912.37,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Because the microlinks is the join online.","index":666,"end_time":2915.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2913.17,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"The data track page.","index":667,"end_time":2916.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2915.05,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Ebay.","index":668,"end_time":2916.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2916.29,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":669,"end_time":2917.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2916.93,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Oh, okay.","index":670,"end_time":2917.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2917.29,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So, so that''s, that''s a terrible way to people to that page.","index":671,"end_time":2923.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2917.85,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What can you show me?","index":672,"end_time":2925.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2924.85,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like what is the form?","index":673,"end_time":2926.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2925.97,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That.","index":674,"end_time":2927.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2927.09,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What is how.","index":675,"end_time":2928.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2927.65,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What different about the trial form is that compared to the regular metaphor?","index":676,"end_time":2933.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2928.25,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"The regular metaphor was so simple.","index":677,"end_time":2934.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2933.12,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"First name, last name, like phone number.","index":678,"end_time":2938.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2935.24,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":679,"end_time":2938.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2938.44,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Email.","index":680,"end_time":2939.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2939.24,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":681,"end_time":2941.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2940.68,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Club, like, like whatever that was.","index":682,"end_time":2943.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2941.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We should look back to what it was before and, and don''t make it more complicated than that because we can always use the campaign.","index":683,"end_time":2951.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2943.32,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Nina, like, tell me if I''m wrong.","index":684,"end_time":2953.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2951.96,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We should be able to track the HubSpot feed down to the campaign that they used.","index":685,"end_time":2958.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2953.4,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":686,"end_time":2959,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2958.64,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"To this campaign.","index":687,"end_time":2960.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2959.36,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So we know that they filled out that campaign.","index":688,"end_time":2964.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2961.84,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We know that they''re a trial.","index":689,"end_time":2965.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2964.64,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":690,"end_time":2966.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2966.24,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So that''s all we need to know.","index":691,"end_time":2968.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2966.76,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because, Milan, does it matter that on their trial form, like they fill out.","index":692,"end_time":2972.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2968.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I''m interested in group fitness, I''m interested in pd.","index":693,"end_time":2975.479,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2972.32,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We should do the same qualification process when we talk to them.","index":694,"end_time":2978,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2975.479,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Every time we add a new question to that form, it creates friction and fewer people will do it.","index":695,"end_time":2983.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2978.48,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":696,"end_time":2984.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2984.24,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"The reason why I added those questions was to get better leads because the trial campaign, when we ran it last time, we got a million, we got a ton of leads, but almost all of them were just crappy.","index":697,"end_time":2998.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2985.91,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I would.","index":698,"end_time":2998.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2998.27,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Instead of.","index":699,"end_time":2999.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2998.87,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So that''s why we added more.","index":700,"end_time":3001.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2999.47,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s also like targeting, you know, targeting like in the, in the, in the geographic radius and doing all that stuff properly.","index":701,"end_time":3009.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3002.55,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But I think like, instead of just focus on one variable, if you do two variables, we''re not going to know.","index":702,"end_time":3015.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3009.19,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Hey, are we not getting leads because the form is long or is it because we did a different kind of promo?","index":703,"end_time":3020.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3015.61,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We''re not going to know that because there''s too many variables.","index":704,"end_time":3022.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3020.53,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So instead for now, keep the form exactly what it was.","index":705,"end_time":3027.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3022.97,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So that way, you know, okay, that, that''s consistent.","index":706,"end_time":3031.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3027.93,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So if anything is better, we know what variable changed instead of like three compounding variables on all changing at once.","index":707,"end_time":3037.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3031.69,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And we''re not going to know like the relationship.","index":708,"end_time":3039.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3037.35,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So change the radius, do whatever you need to in front of targeting to make sure we get the right people.","index":709,"end_time":3044.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3039.87,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Keep the form as simple as possible and we will deal with the qualifications later.","index":710,"end_time":3050.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3044.91,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We can adjust that, but what we can''t have is like it has three more questions on it and now people like don''t even complete the form.","index":711,"end_time":3056.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3050.43,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So that''s.","index":712,"end_time":3057.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3057.39,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So we should keep the same form and then don''t take them to the microlinks, just use the methods.","index":713,"end_time":3065.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3057.99,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because that''s how we get leads all through time is people just fill out a form.","index":714,"end_time":3069.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3065.34,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That''s how we get the lead.","index":715,"end_time":3071.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3069.94,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We don''t take them to a place where we don''t get their lead because our website isn''t built out.","index":716,"end_time":3075.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3071.22,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"The join page is confusing.","index":717,"end_time":3077.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3075.54,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Can we have it so that like for example, they, they complete the, the, the meta form, we collect all their information and then it directs them to the micro link.","index":718,"end_time":3089.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3078.42,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I would have to check that.","index":719,"end_time":3095.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3094.15,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I''m not sure.","index":720,"end_time":3096.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3095.59,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I think.","index":721,"end_time":3097.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3097.19,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s fine, that''s fine.","index":722,"end_time":3098.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3097.63,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We just need to get their lead no matter at all cost here.","index":723,"end_time":3101.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3098.87,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like if we have 25 leads but 10 of them aren''t right, we know the work we need to do.","index":724,"end_time":3107.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3101.31,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"If we have no leads, we have no idea what''s happening.","index":725,"end_time":3110.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3107.51,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right, right, right, right.","index":726,"end_time":3113.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3111.67,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like it''s a different kind of problem set to work on.","index":727,"end_time":3116.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3113.19,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So is that something you can do, Nina?","index":728,"end_time":3118.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3116.74,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like as soon as possible?","index":729,"end_time":3119.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3118.02,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like right now, these are, these, these to me are like dead ads.","index":730,"end_time":3122.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3119.14,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They''re taking them to like, like a dead place right now, those links.","index":731,"end_time":3129.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3122.74,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So just have them direct to the form.","index":732,"end_time":3130.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3129.34,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"The most important thing we need to do our ads is getting their phone number and their email.","index":733,"end_time":3137.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3131.22,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"However way we do that, it''s not like anything else.","index":734,"end_time":3140.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3137.46,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They can look at our website afterwards.","index":735,"end_time":3143.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3141.22,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But if we, if they don''t give us their lead then it''s sort of like not, you know, it''s not helpful.","index":736,"end_time":3149.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3143.14,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":737,"end_time":3150.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3150.12,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"One thing that I would suggest, I mean we can change the forms to be shorter and to be more basic.","index":738,"end_time":3158.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3151.08,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"But I agree with Milan that it''s good to have some information about the lead.","index":739,"end_time":3162.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3158.4,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So for example, since Arc, the trial campaign is kind of created around like learning more about the person that''s entering, that''s trying to join to, to have the salespeople maybe still ask those questions just so you have those properties.","index":740,"end_time":3176.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3162.6,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Because it does make it easier to sign somebody actually up for.","index":741,"end_time":3180.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3176.82,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Let''s do that on the call but not on the form because we should still be able to track the lead to the campaign.","index":742,"end_time":3187.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3181.66,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":743,"end_time":3187.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3187.58,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So HubSpot, we''ll know this person came from trial.","index":744,"end_time":3190.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3187.9,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Let''s ask them some random other questions.","index":745,"end_time":3192.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3190.38,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We, our rep should be doing that on the phone, but not on the metaphor.","index":746,"end_time":3196.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3192.46,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"The metaphor is almost like you''re interested, click a button.","index":747,"end_time":3200.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3197.02,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It should be that simple.","index":748,"end_time":3202.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3201.59,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"No thinking.","index":749,"end_time":3203.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3202.87,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because they''re scrolling through, they''re not thinking about giving us all this information.","index":750,"end_time":3206.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3203.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They, it just is like that.","index":751,"end_time":3209.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3207.19,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Whatever it was before, I think we should also, in that whatever was before, we had them select.","index":752,"end_time":3215.109,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3209.91,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":753,"end_time":3215.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3215.51,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Which club.","index":754,"end_time":3216.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3215.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So I''ll leave that up to you, Nina.","index":755,"end_time":3218.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3217.59,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"If you think that if they hit the.","index":756,"end_time":3221.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3218.95,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think the, the reason, the rationale was if they see the Miami ad.","index":757,"end_time":3225.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3221.51,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":758,"end_time":3226.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3226.18,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It doesn''t mean that they live in Miami.","index":759,"end_time":3229.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3226.66,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They could just be there for some time and they see the ad.","index":760,"end_time":3233.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3229.86,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So that''s why on the forum we thought it was most like, like the best option was to still have them select which club because they might not even know that we have two clubs.","index":761,"end_time":3244.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3233.3,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Does that make sense?","index":762,"end_time":3246.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3245.3,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So we don''t need to create like, here''s the Miami form, here''s the, this different form.","index":763,"end_time":3251.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3246.26,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But give.","index":764,"end_time":3252.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3251.87,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"One of the questions in the, in the additional.","index":765,"end_time":3254.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3252.47,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"In a metaphor was like, select the club that you''re interested in.","index":766,"end_time":3257.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3254.79,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So we''ll still have it.","index":767,"end_time":3259.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3258.51,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Go to the right club, but we just won''t need to like run multiple, like very variations of that form.","index":768,"end_time":3264.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3259.55,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":769,"end_time":3267.469,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3266.989,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay.","index":770,"end_time":3268.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3267.47,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Well, let''s.","index":771,"end_time":3269.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3269.07,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Nina, you had a, you had a reasoning why we split those forms where it was just by club.","index":772,"end_time":3275.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3270.43,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"This.","index":773,"end_time":3277.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3277,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"What was the reason again?","index":774,"end_time":3278.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3277.8,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It was because it was easier to track.","index":775,"end_time":3280.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3278.76,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Which.","index":776,"end_time":3280.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3280.44,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s easier to track the leads.","index":777,"end_time":3283.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3280.84,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And also, I mean, I, for people that are signing up, it doesn''t make more sense because, for example, if somebody''s just in Miami and they''re seeing an ad because they''re in.","index":778,"end_time":3292.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3283.2,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Within that location, they''re probably not going to sign up for a gym while they''re there.","index":779,"end_time":3297.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3292.64,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"But I mean, just because somebody sees an ad doesn''t mean that they''re interested.","index":780,"end_time":3303.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3297.84,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"But yeah, it''s usually better for tracking.","index":781,"end_time":3307.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3305.08,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"It''s better for knowing, like, what kind of leads you''re getting, what kind of people are interested.","index":782,"end_time":3312.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3307.36,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Like, it''s easier for sales people.","index":783,"end_time":3314.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3312.4,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"It''s.","index":784,"end_time":3315.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3314.68,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s not though, because, I mean, tell me if I''m wrong.","index":785,"end_time":3317.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3315.12,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, like Fort Lauderdale, Miami are so close together.","index":786,"end_time":3320.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3317.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They''re so close together.","index":787,"end_time":3321.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3320.84,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Someone who sees the Miami ad, look at the, look at the ad itself.","index":788,"end_time":3325.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3322.36,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"The ad itself doesn''t always say Miami, Miami.","index":789,"end_time":3329.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3325.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s just some of them might just be powerhouse.","index":790,"end_time":3331.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3329.32,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right?","index":791,"end_time":3332.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3332.07,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, yeah, yeah, go ahead.","index":792,"end_time":3335.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3332.79,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But for example, a Miami ad might cost you more than a fourth Lauderdale ad because it''s a different radius.","index":793,"end_time":3344.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3335.91,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yes, yes.","index":794,"end_time":3348.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3347.03,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That''s why we have these ad sets.","index":795,"end_time":3350.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3348.31,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":796,"end_time":3350.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3350.31,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That''s why we see it.","index":797,"end_time":3351.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3350.47,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But I''m, I''m talking about like on the form itself.","index":798,"end_time":3354.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3351.75,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s not that important.","index":799,"end_time":3355.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3354.39,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I guess the question is, should we give them the option to select the club in the form or should we not and just say that anyone who fills a form, if it, if we on the Miami ad would then go to the Miami rep?","index":800,"end_time":3374.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3361.36,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I''m saying, like, that is not a good idea.","index":801,"end_time":3378.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3376.4,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because since we started, we haven''t really needed to do that.","index":802,"end_time":3384.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3380.48,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because when they look at the Miami ad, it''s not like it''s obviously, oh, this is Miami.","index":803,"end_time":3391.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3384.77,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It, it might be.","index":804,"end_time":3392.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3391.81,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"This is Fort Lauderdale as well.","index":805,"end_time":3394.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3392.69,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s.","index":806,"end_time":3395.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3395.33,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It could be mixed.","index":807,"end_time":3396.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3395.73,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Or if they see the Fort Lauderdale, they could be interested in Miami.","index":808,"end_time":3399.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3396.73,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So they fill out that.","index":809,"end_time":3401.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3400.21,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"If they fill out that form, that lead is going to jump to our rep in Fort Lauderdale versus if we had the user just select which club they''re interested in.","index":810,"end_time":3410.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3401.29,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That''s the, you know, that''s what we had before.","index":811,"end_time":3411.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3410.29,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Then we know 100% that our Miami rep should be talking to this person.","index":812,"end_time":3418.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3412.74,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Does that make sense?","index":813,"end_time":3419.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3418.74,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"If we had one gym club, it only goes to one, but we have two.","index":814,"end_time":3426.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3422.74,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So we need to know where the user wants to be, who they want to be contacted with.","index":815,"end_time":3432.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3427.22,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because our ads isn''t going to be always like, here''s our Fort Lauderdale one.","index":816,"end_time":3438.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3432.78,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because somebody might see that ad and they are working in Fort Lauderdale.","index":817,"end_time":3442.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3438.58,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They spend eight hours a day in Fort Lauderdale, but they live in Miami or vice versa.","index":818,"end_time":3447.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3443.01,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We have no way to know that.","index":819,"end_time":3448.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3447.09,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So we kind of have to have them qualify themselves in the beginning.","index":820,"end_time":3453.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3449.41,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Otherwise they might just think like, oh, this is the Miami club.","index":821,"end_time":3457.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3453.57,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t live there.","index":822,"end_time":3458.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3457.77,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I live in Fort Lauderdale.","index":823,"end_time":3460.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3459.17,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But they just, they fill in a form, but it''s us who knows which look like the form itself is for our purpose to track the data.","index":824,"end_time":3471.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3461.33,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Like, the lead form doesn''t say, hey, this is the lead gen Miami form.","index":825,"end_time":3476.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3471.82,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"When we get the, when they fill out the form, we have to ask them, which club are you interested in?","index":826,"end_time":3486.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3479.18,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":827,"end_time":3487.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3487.1,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because if, if that form defaults to Miami, let''s say form one defaults to Miami.","index":828,"end_time":3492.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3487.46,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They don''t live in Miami.","index":829,"end_time":3495.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3494.05,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They just see that form, they''re gonna think, and then our rep is gonna call them, and then turns out they''re.","index":830,"end_time":3504.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3495.29,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Not going to like, I, I understand the logic.","index":831,"end_time":3509.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3504.17,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"It''s Just that for example, when they see a lead gen form that has a selection box.","index":832,"end_time":3515.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3509.89,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So for example, you can select Miami or for Fort Lauderdale.","index":833,"end_time":3519.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3515.93,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":834,"end_time":3519.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3519.46,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":835,"end_time":3520.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3519.82,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"They know that there are those two locations.","index":836,"end_time":3522.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3520.18,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"But when they go to an ad that has, that''s targeting the Miami radius and they go to the lead gen form, the lead gen form doesn''t ask them.","index":837,"end_time":3533.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3522.46,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Like they don''t.","index":838,"end_time":3534.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3533.54,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"There''s no reason.","index":839,"end_time":3536.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3534.619,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m saying it should though.","index":840,"end_time":3538.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3536.7,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Why, why should it not ask them?","index":841,"end_time":3539.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3538.06,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because it''s just a legion form.","index":842,"end_time":3542.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3540.78,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Like they don''t.","index":843,"end_time":3543.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3542.46,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"But it''s not you.","index":844,"end_time":3544.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3543.34,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Do you see the legion flows into our reps job.","index":845,"end_time":3547.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3544.1,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":846,"end_time":3547.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3547.38,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So if they fill out a form and this person actually would prefer Fort Lauderdale experience, then our Miami sales rep should not be contacting them.","index":847,"end_time":3558.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3548.1,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s our Florida sales rep or our Fort Lauderdale sales rep should be calling them and saying, let me schedule you for a visit.","index":848,"end_time":3563.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3558.5,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"My name is so and so.","index":849,"end_time":3564.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3563.74,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":850,"end_time":3565.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3565.14,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But how often does that happen?","index":851,"end_time":3567.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3565.54,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I mean I, I don''t think it happens that often or I know it doesn''t happen because we have never had.","index":852,"end_time":3578.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3571.07,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"To deal with it.","index":853,"end_time":3578.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3578.11,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We never had to deal with it because all of our forms historically have always asked the user, what club are you interested in?","index":854,"end_time":3586.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3578.75,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We''ve always asked the user that.","index":855,"end_time":3588.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3586.51,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So if you change it now to just it''s only Miami, like it defaults to Miami, then we''re going to start perhaps seeing this stuff.","index":856,"end_time":3595.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3588.91,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Either way we''re tracking it.","index":857,"end_time":3597.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3595.79,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right?","index":858,"end_time":3597.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3597.23,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We''re not not tracking it, we''re just talking about the ux.","index":859,"end_time":3600.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3597.47,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That''s all we''re talking about.","index":860,"end_time":3601.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3600.72,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":861,"end_time":3602.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3601.96,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We''re not not tracking it because we''re going to, it''s always going to show up in HubSpot as a club that, that lead, which club, which club should be that lead.","index":862,"end_time":3610.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3602.48,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":863,"end_time":3611.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3611.04,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"My thing is like I think someone else told me said and I think it was like, I don''t know if it''s FMR or the one after Milan.","index":864,"end_time":3618.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3612.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They said people don''t know that you have multiple clubs.","index":865,"end_time":3622.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3618.92,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They have no idea.","index":866,"end_time":3624.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3623.04,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And if on the form you ask them optically, it will tell them that we have different locations.","index":867,"end_time":3630.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3624.49,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So we give people the optics of well, which one?","index":868,"end_time":3633.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3630.89,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"There''s something powerful about that because we have multiple clubs.","index":869,"end_time":3637.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3633.77,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":870,"end_time":3638.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3638.01,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You know what I mean?","index":871,"end_time":3640.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3639.53,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, like they again think about someone who.","index":872,"end_time":3644.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3640.37,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"The two towns are could be like 20 minutes away, 15 minutes away, 20 minutes away.","index":873,"end_time":3649.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3644.41,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But if you work, if you live in one and many people, how many people live in one city and work in the other.","index":874,"end_time":3655.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3650.42,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"There''S a, there''s a decent Amount?","index":875,"end_time":3659.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3657.94,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s.","index":876,"end_time":3661.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3659.62,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It there.","index":877,"end_time":3661.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3661.5,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, there''s a decent amount.","index":878,"end_time":3663.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3662.1,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s not as close as 20 minutes, but yeah, it does happen.","index":879,"end_time":3667.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3663.26,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I mean, depending on where you are right there, there''s a lot.","index":880,"end_time":3670.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3667.38,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So I think if you, if, you know, it''s like if they live in one or work in the other, there''s no way we''re going to get this right.","index":881,"end_time":3677.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3670.26,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Just think about it, Nina.","index":882,"end_time":3678.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3677.19,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, there''s no way.","index":883,"end_time":3679.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3678.35,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because someone could see this ad while they''re working in Miami, but they actually don''t want to.","index":884,"end_time":3685.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3679.63,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They don''t want to have a.","index":885,"end_time":3686.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3685.23,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They don''t want to actually have a gym in Miami.","index":886,"end_time":3688.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3686.43,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So.","index":887,"end_time":3689.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3689.15,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So they''re on their Instagram at 5pm, at 7pm out, dinner with friends, and they fill out this.","index":888,"end_time":3694.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3689.47,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And our Miami rep calls them.","index":889,"end_time":3695.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3694.11,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Do you see the issue here?","index":890,"end_time":3699.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3698.59,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s like they.","index":891,"end_time":3700.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3700.03,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Our mind''s like, oh, you actually prefer for Lauderdale.","index":892,"end_time":3703.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3701.08,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Let me connect you to my Fort Lauderdale sales rep. Now.","index":893,"end_time":3706.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3703.08,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We just created extra work on our side to have to pass this person to a different club because there''s so many people that live in one and work in the other, vice versa.","index":894,"end_time":3716.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3706.28,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So I think we have to ask that question.","index":895,"end_time":3718.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3716.48,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So do you want the creative also to be just generic and not mention any location at all?","index":896,"end_time":3724.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3718.28,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"No, that''s the opposite.","index":897,"end_time":3725.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3724.44,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I''m saying, like, it should mention the.","index":898,"end_time":3727.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3725.6,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It should mention.","index":899,"end_time":3728.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3727.28,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Give them the option, which club are you interested in?","index":900,"end_time":3730.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3728.28,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Just look back to the form.","index":901,"end_time":3731.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3730.74,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We just.","index":902,"end_time":3731.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3731.58,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"She''s asking the creative, she''s asking the creator.","index":903,"end_time":3735.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3732.54,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Like the, like the actual ad itself, not the form.","index":904,"end_time":3739.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3736.62,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So for example, the copy.","index":905,"end_time":3741.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3740.22,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":906,"end_time":3743.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3742.86,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So I think that''s okay.","index":907,"end_time":3744.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3743.42,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think that''s okay.","index":908,"end_time":3745.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3744.86,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You can make it location specific for that one.","index":909,"end_time":3748.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3745.86,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Just a form is going to give them the option because.","index":910,"end_time":3754.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3749.9,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":911,"end_time":3755.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3755.38,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That they might see it, but they''re not gonna, you know, we should probably have all three.","index":912,"end_time":3760.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3755.54,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We should have like a creative which is Miami based, a creative which is Fort Lauderdale based, and then a creative which is a generic one.","index":913,"end_time":3768.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3760.42,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":914,"end_time":3768.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3768.5,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Where it''s not.","index":915,"end_time":3769.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3768.94,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Where it''s not location specific.","index":916,"end_time":3771.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3769.7,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"All the ad forms will just add the Miami and Fort Lauderdale option.","index":917,"end_time":3777.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3771.86,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":918,"end_time":3780.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3780.1,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then.","index":919,"end_time":3781.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3781.39,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":920,"end_time":3782.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3782.43,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"As long as it doesn''t affect the.","index":921,"end_time":3784.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3782.95,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"The tracking aspect.","index":922,"end_time":3786.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3784.59,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Which both won''t.","index":923,"end_time":3789.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3786.31,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s just one is gonna, One''s gonna qualify them early for you.","index":924,"end_time":3791.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3789.03,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Milan.","index":925,"end_time":3792.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3791.79,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"One''s gonna be like, you know that they, they put FTL they selected.","index":926,"end_time":3796.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3792.27,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":927,"end_time":3796.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3796.27,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"There''s no question of does this person actually want ftl?","index":928,"end_time":3800.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3796.55,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Do they want Miami?","index":929,"end_time":3801.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3800.11,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You know, it''ll be what they selected.","index":930,"end_time":3805.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3802.19,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, but we don''t need to ask them on the forum.","index":931,"end_time":3808.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3806.11,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, I don''t know if we already do this.","index":932,"end_time":3810.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3808.87,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What''s your interest?","index":933,"end_time":3810.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3810.19,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What is your, you know, any of that stuff?","index":934,"end_time":3813.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3811.23,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because people don''t like to.","index":935,"end_time":3814.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3813.23,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They barely like to type their email and phone number in general.","index":936,"end_time":3817.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3814.67,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I mean, it.","index":937,"end_time":3818.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3818.27,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"It depends.","index":938,"end_time":3819.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3818.87,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Like, if it''s just a weightlifting gym.","index":939,"end_time":3821.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3819.35,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"}],"dateString":"2026-01-21T16:00:00.000Z","host_email":"nina.belina@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/86061042503?pwd=x0TBEgRs7qFmrRIEItauCzbH71kaq8.1","participants":["yefei@yhatinvest.com,alex.white@yhatinvest.com,tatiana@powerhousegymsoflo.com,wyattc@yhatinvest.com,robert.rudder@powerhousesoflo.com,colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com,tatiana.fernandez@powerhousesoflo.com,milan.wagner@powerhousesoflo.com,nina.belina@marketersindemand.com,cristina@pgmia.com,milan@pgmia.com","yefei@yhatinvest.com","alex.white@yhatinvest.com","tatiana@powerhousegymsoflo.com","wyattc@yhatinvest.com","robert.rudder@powerhousesoflo.com","colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com","tatiana.fernandez@powerhousesoflo.com","milan.wagner@powerhousesoflo.com","cristina@pgmia.com","milan@pgmia.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01KEZ30C05BHAMFY5M5SYW7QB7","organizer_email":"nina.belina@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
    '{"label":"positive","confidence":0.87,"bullets":["Resolved access issues for Meta pixel sharing to enable lead attribution into HubSpot.","Agreed to simplify Meta lead forms to improve submission rates and reduce user friction.","Decided to collect user preferences for club location within Meta forms to streamline routing.","Committed to removing microlinks to ensure all ad traffic captures lead data effectively.","Planned parallel work on tracking, analytics, and CRM integrations during website updates."],"highlights":[{"quote":"Want me to go to events manager or are you guys going to set up the rest?","speaker":"Milan Wagner"},{"quote":"We just need to get their lead no matter at all cost here.","speaker":"Yefei Jin"},{"quote":"We can change the forms to be shorter and to be more basic.","speaker":"Nina Belina"}],"topics":["ads","crm","forms","tracking","delivery"],"model":"openai/gpt-4","version":1,"generated_at":"2026-01-24T00:00:00Z"}'::jsonb,
    '{"fireflies_summary":{"notes":"## **Meta Pixel Integration and Data Tracking**\n\nThe team resolved critical access issues with the **Meta pixel sharing** between **Meta** and **HubSpot**, enabling accurate campaign data tracking (06:00).\n\n- **Nina Belina** and **Milan Wagner** coordinated to add the correct users and permissions, granting full control to avoid repeated setup.\n- The pixel integration will allow visibility of lead sources directly in HubSpot, linking each lead to the originating campaign.\n- Developers will finalize the technical setup, including pixel assignments and custom conversions, to improve campaign attribution accuracy.\n- This integration is essential to measure campaign ROI precisely and optimize paid media spending by tracking lead origins.\n\n## **Website Contact and Membership Form Strategy**\n\nThe team agreed to maintain the current **contact form’s look and feel** while ensuring data flows seamlessly into HubSpot without using clunky HubSpot form embeds on the new **Framer-built website** (15:25).\n\n- **Yefei Jin** emphasized using a native Framer form that preserves design aesthetics but pushes data to HubSpot, avoiding embedded scripts.\n- The membership “Join” form’s user experience will shift from a pop-up to potentially a dedicated landing page to reduce friction (20:51).\n- Pre-filling form data for users on the membership page is unlikely due to security protocols, so the team will explore alternative ways to shorten the lead capture path.\n- Nina will consult developers about form workflows and integration feasibility to ensure compliance with privacy and terms policy inclusion.\n\n## **Paid Media Campaign Performance and Lead Quality**\n\nCurrent paid campaigns include two **dollar down** and two **trial experience campaigns**, all recently approved and in the learning phase, showing limited lead volume but early impressions data (30:19).\n\n- The team noted that campaigns driving traffic to microlinks rather than direct lead forms cause lead capture gaps, resulting in zero leads despite clicks.\n- **Yefei Jin** highlighted that Meta lead forms provide direct cost-per-lead metrics, unlike campaigns funneling to landing pages, which complicates ROI tracking.\n- The trial experience form was lengthened to improve lead qualification, but **Yefei** recommended reverting to shorter forms to reduce drop-offs and isolate targeting variables.\n- Nina will prioritize redirecting ads to Meta lead forms that capture emails and phone numbers immediately, ensuring lead acquisition is the primary goal.\n\n## **Lead Qualification and Club Selection Logic**\n\nThe team decided to keep **club selection (Miami vs. Fort Lauderdale)** as a mandatory field on lead forms to ensure leads are routed correctly to sales reps and reduce confusion (59:00).\n\n- **Yefei Jin** stressed the importance of users self-identifying their preferred club given the proximity and overlap between locations.\n- The ads will remain location-specific, but the form will explicitly ask users to select their club, allowing accurate lead assignment and reducing internal lead handoffs.\n- Maintaining club selection on forms also educates leads about multiple locations, improving brand awareness and engagement.\n- Nina confirmed that this approach aligns with tracking needs and supports sales team workflows without disrupting campaign attribution.\n\n## **Process Improvements and Next Steps**\n\nThe team agreed on process improvements to enhance lead capture and tracking effectiveness immediately (51:18).\n\n- Nina to shorten and simplify lead forms on Meta campaigns to reduce friction while retaining core data capture fields.\n- Milan to follow up with **Amanda** at DataTrack regarding abandoned cart lead integration and possible form pre-fill solutions.\n- Nina to gather developer input on website form-to-HubSpot workflows, privacy policy inclusion, and analytics/pixel implementation.\n- Paid media specialist to remain engaged indirectly; Nina will relay questions and updates to ensure campaign adjustments align with lead capture goals.","outline":null,"keywords":["Meta pixel","HubSpot integration","lead capture","ad campaign tracking","membership forms","club selection"],"overview":"- **Meta Pixel Integration:** Resolved pixel sharing issue for accurate campaign tracking in HubSpot; critical for measuring ROI.  \n- **Form Strategy:** Maintain contact form design, using native Framer forms to push data into HubSpot without embedded scripts.  \n- **Campaign Performance:** Current paid campaigns showing limited leads; direct Meta lead forms needed for better cost-per-lead metrics.  \n- **Lead Qualification:** Mandatory club selection on forms ensures correct lead routing and enhances brand awareness for multiple locations.  \n- **Process Improvements:** Shortening lead forms and exploring pre-fill options; prioritize seamless integration with HubSpot and effective analytics.","action_items":"\n**Nina Belina**\nResolve pixel sharing setup and permissions with Milan (11:38)\nVerify with developer the workflow and tech details for integrating the Framer contact form on new website with HubSpot lead capture (19:30)\nResearch possibilities to shorten the user path with microlinks to avoid users filling out multiple forms (25:00)\nRequest and share email for editor access to framework developers for website analytics, pixel integration, and SEO preparation (29:16)\nAdjust current Meta campaigns to direct traffic to lead forms instead of microlinks for more effective lead capture (52:30)\nShorten and simplify lead forms on Meta for trial campaigns, maintaining essential fields like club selection (53:46)\nCoordinate with Meta paid media specialist to switch all campaign lead capture to Meta forms to allow consistent cost per lead metrics (46:32)\n\n**Milan Wagner**\nFollow up with Amanda at DataTrack on abandoned cart lead capture capabilities and report back (27:42)\n\n**Yefei Jin**\nAnalyze lead capture flow and ad performance data alongside Nina to optimize tracking setup during campaign learning phase (46:32)\n\n**Nina Belina & Milan Wagner**\nPrepare three ad creative variants (Miami, Fort Lauderdale, generic), ensuring all forms include club selection field (01:02:40)\n\n**Sales team**\nConduct further lead qualification calls to capture additional lead data beyond initial Meta form submission (01:02:40)\n"},"migrated_from":"contract_meetings","original_id":"2871d441-55dc-4358-8f83-cda90e64fca7","master_marketer":{"status":"migrated"}}'::jsonb,
