    NULL,
    '{"id":"01KFPDPB49K4YNJWQVEHD6MSFY","title":"Hydrian x New North Weekly Meeting 01.21.26","summary":{"notes":"## **Survey Response and Engagement Strategy**\n\nThe team plans to boost survey participation by changing distribution methods and considering incentives to improve response rates.\n\n- **Two new survey responses** arrived after the latest reminder, showing ongoing engagement but at about **50% of the previous response volume** (03:45)\n    - Switching the survey email domain aims to reduce messages landing in spam folders for the next distribution.\n    - Bailey noted mixed answer consistency, with the current survey showing more varied responses than the initial one.\n    - The survey will be linked through HubSpot in the upcoming newsletter and also sent via Mailchimp to broaden audience reach.\n    - Offering a **$50 gift card** prize in a draw was proposed as a low-cost incentive to increase participation, pending further discussion with Josh.\n\n- The team now has access to detailed **open and unopened email stats**, improving transparency compared to previous blind spots (06:28)\n    - SurveyMonkey’s new analytics help identify who responds and who might miss the survey due to spam filters.\n    - These insights support refining future survey outreach to improve engagement rates.\n\n## **Booth and Brochure Messaging Alignment**\n\nEfforts are underway to refresh booth materials to better reflect current messaging and improve readability for trade shows.\n\n- The **brochure text was condensed and rewritten** to align with the website’s messaging and make it punchier for quick scanning at events (09:04)\n    - The goal is to communicate clearly what the company does in simple terms visible to passersby.\n    - Shorter, bigger text replaces dense paragraphs to encourage scanning and engagement.\n    - Graphics and icons are being reviewed for consistency with the website’s current style, aiming for brand cohesion.\n    - Bailey emphasized the need to reflect the company’s advisory role rather than just software features, highlighting evolving customer expectations.\n\n- The booth design and brochure final files are being prepared for print after incorporating these edits (07:46)\n    - Design fixes include reducing white space and enlarging fonts for better legibility.\n    - The survey links in the newsletter now feature a colored bar for visibility, a format planned for reuse in future editions.\n\n## **Strategic Positioning and Client Communication**\n\nThe team is adjusting the company’s positioning from a software vendor to a hybrid advisory and technology partner, based on client feedback and market needs.\n\n- Bailey explained that clients want **clear guidance and actionable advice**, not just software tools, reflecting a shift toward a consultative approach (13:07)\n    - The company is increasingly asked to advise on process changes and task execution, blending technology with advisory services.\n    - This hybrid model differentiates the company from pure software providers and pure consulting firms.\n    - Messaging updates aim to reflect this dual role clearly, reducing client confusion and aligning sales and marketing communications.\n\n- Consistency across website, brochures, and sales conversations is a priority to avoid mixed messages during client interactions (15:44)\n    - This alignment is critical to maintain trust and clarity throughout the buyer journey.\n    - QR codes on brochures lead to additional assets that reinforce this messaging strategy.\n\n## **Client Testimonials and Content Development**\n\nBuilding a stronger pipeline of client testimonials and case studies is recognized as vital to supporting sales and marketing efforts.\n\n- The team identified a need for **more testimonials and case studies**, including anonymous formats to respect client confidentiality (17:02)\n    - Bailey plans to discuss testimonial opportunities with Josh, especially with clients like Imperial, despite some approval challenges.\n    - Third-party interviews were suggested as a low-pressure way to gather authentic client stories.\n    - Taylor and Bailey see these as key content assets to showcase results and build credibility.\n\n- These testimonials will be repurposed across website content and social media, including carousel posts to highlight client success (18:25)\n    - Drafts for carousel post copy are being finalized and will be shared for review soon.\n    - This content will help communicate the company’s value proposition more vividly on social channels.\n\n## **Process and Collaboration Improvements**\n\nThe team is improving feedback handling and collaborative document management to streamline design and messaging workflows.\n\n- Moving to a **markup-based feedback system** will simplify managing multiple rounds of design comments and revisions (22:10)\n    - This change will reduce confusion from scattered feedback and improve document clarity.\n    - Michael will consolidate all design notes into a single markup file for easier review and version control.\n    - The team agreed this approach is more user-friendly, especially given the volume of feedback involved.\n\n- Upcoming meetings will focus on strategic brainstorming and reviewing the goals document to refine direction further (19:39)\n    - Josh’s participation is mandatory to ensure alignment and full team input.\n    - The meetings aim to integrate new ideas with existing plans, allowing for iterative improvements in strategy and execution.","outline":null,"keywords":["SurveyMonkey","Newsletter Design","Brochure Revision","Client Testimonials","Social Media Carousel","Strategy Session"],"overview":"- **Survey Participation and Engagement:** New methods and a $50 gift card incentive aim to improve survey response rates, at 50% of prior levels.\n\n- **Booth Material Refresh:** Brochures are rewritten to align with website messaging, emphasizing clearer communication for trade shows.\n\n- **Positioning as Advisory Partners:** Company shifts focus to offer actionable advice alongside technology, enhancing client trust and clarity in communications.\n\n- **Client Testimonials Development:** Need for more testimonials recognized; plans for anonymous formats and third-party interviews to build credibility.\n\n- **Feedback Process Improvements:** New markup system will streamline document feedback and revisions, aiding clarity and version control in design workflows.","action_items":"\n**Michael**\nMonitor incoming SurveyMonkey responses and provide updated PDF by Friday with current data (03:45)\nSwitch survey domain in next distribution to avoid spam folder issues (03:45)\nFinalize newsletter edits with design team, adjusting layout, font size, and white space issues (07:46)\nSend revised brochure text and comments separately for review, ensuring improved alignment with website messaging (09:04)\nReview website icon library and propose updated graphics for brochure consistency (11:38)\nSend markup links for all design files to facilitate easy commenting and review (22:10)\nPrepare final booth design files for print and share with team (19:20)\nShare copy outline for social media carousel posts for client edits later in the day (19:39)\nDiscuss client testimonial opportunities and permissions with Josh; report back with updates (17:02)\nParticipate in next week’s brainstorming and strategy session, prepare to review referral partnership and goals document (20:50)\n\n**Taylor Doerbaum**\nCoordinate inclusion of survey link in new newsletter via HubSpot and Mailchimp distribution lists to increase response rates (05:50)\nCoordinate testimonial collection from clients, including offering anonymous Zoom interviews (17:02)\nReview attached final design templates and provide feedback (19:20)\nReview social media carousel post copy and provide edits or suggestions as needed (19:39)\nAttend next brainstorming and strategy session, ensure Josh’s attendance (20:50)\n"},"duration":23.100000381469727,"speakers":[],"sentences":[{"text":"Hello.","index":0,"end_time":62.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":62.1,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Hey.","index":1,"end_time":63.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":62.98,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How''s it going?","index":2,"end_time":65.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":64.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Going good.","index":3,"end_time":66.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":65.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is it rough being back after a long trip?","index":4,"end_time":70.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":67.86,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"No, it, like, yes and no.","index":5,"end_time":74.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":72.42,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like, all the emails and the messages, it''s like, huh.","index":6,"end_time":79.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":76.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So many things to review.","index":7,"end_time":81.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":80.01,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But, like, yeah, after a long trip, it''s, like, good to sleep in my own bed again.","index":8,"end_time":86.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":81.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, that''s true.","index":9,"end_time":88.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":87.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":10,"end_time":88.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":88.33,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Do you feel like you''re used to your new hair?","index":11,"end_time":94.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":91.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like, you''ve been blonde for so long.","index":12,"end_time":96.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":94.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Are you, like.","index":13,"end_time":96.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":96.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s funny.","index":14,"end_time":98.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":97.53,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''m already, like, itching to go back to blonde, which my mom always told me when I first dyed it blonde.","index":15,"end_time":105.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":99.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"She''s like, you''re gonna become, like, a blonde junkie, and you''re gonna always, like, want to keep it up.","index":16,"end_time":109.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":105.81,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I was like, you''re right.","index":17,"end_time":111,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":109.37,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You''re right.","index":18,"end_time":111.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":111,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then I did brown, and now I''m like, I want to go back.","index":19,"end_time":114.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":111.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I do like it.","index":20,"end_time":115.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":114.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s.","index":21,"end_time":115.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":115.24,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think it''s a good change, and I''ve wanted to do it for a couple of years now, so I''m glad I did it.","index":22,"end_time":120.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":115.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But I don''t know.","index":23,"end_time":122.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":122.04,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I just really.","index":24,"end_time":123.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":122.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I have such thin hair, and I think that the blonde hides that better because when there''s, like, dimension and highlight.","index":25,"end_time":129.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":123.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":26,"end_time":130.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":129.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think it helps because you can, like, see how thin my hair is.","index":27,"end_time":133.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":130.44,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think way more when it''s brown.","index":28,"end_time":136.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":133.84,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So.","index":29,"end_time":136.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":136.5,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So.","index":30,"end_time":137.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":136.81,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So, yeah, like, I need to go back to blonde, so we''ll see.","index":31,"end_time":144.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":138.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But I need to give my hair a little bit of a break, I think, like, in.","index":32,"end_time":146.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":144.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, April or something.","index":33,"end_time":148.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":146.97,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"My brother''s getting married in June, and I''m in that wedding, so maybe.","index":34,"end_time":152.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":148.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Oh, that''s exciting.","index":35,"end_time":153.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":152.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yes, so that''s exciting.","index":36,"end_time":157.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":154.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Always stressful to change the hair, but at least you can say you did it now.","index":37,"end_time":161.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":157.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, that''s true.","index":38,"end_time":163.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":162.42,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''s true.","index":39,"end_time":163.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":163.1,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"All right.","index":40,"end_time":164.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":164.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Sorry about that.","index":41,"end_time":165.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":164.46,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"No worries.","index":42,"end_time":166.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":165.86,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I couldn''t get into Zoom.","index":43,"end_time":168.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":166.82,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I had to go through the browser, so.","index":44,"end_time":170.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":168.22,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, I had an issue with Zoom yesterday too.","index":45,"end_time":173.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":171.14,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It wouldn''t load any.","index":46,"end_time":174.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":173.98,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"My meeting.","index":47,"end_time":175.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":174.94,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I had to change the whole link, so I just.","index":48,"end_time":178.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":175.42,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''ve been here before.","index":49,"end_time":179.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":178.74,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I know.","index":50,"end_time":180.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":180.1,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We know Zoom, don''t we?","index":51,"end_time":182.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":180.82,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Gosh.","index":52,"end_time":182.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":182.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Hello, everyone.","index":53,"end_time":183.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":182.86,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Well, Josh won''t be joining us, by the way, just to let you know.","index":54,"end_time":186.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":183.62,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay, yeah, no worries.","index":55,"end_time":189.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":186.82,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''ll go ahead and get started.","index":56,"end_time":190.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":189.15,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I was just pulling up your email.","index":57,"end_time":191.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":190.03,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I know you just sent that over, so I''ll.","index":58,"end_time":194.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":191.43,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''ll pull that up when we get to that point of shirs.","index":59,"end_time":197.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":194.23,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But you can tell how.","index":60,"end_time":199.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":197.51,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You can tell which ones I started with and which one I ended with because it became less and Less messy, more.","index":61,"end_time":204.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":199.39,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I realized, oh, I could do this rather than that.","index":62,"end_time":207.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":204.71,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I apologize, dude.","index":63,"end_time":209.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":207.55,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Doesn''t make any sense.","index":64,"end_time":210.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":209.51,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You.","index":65,"end_time":210.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":210.51,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''ll take the whole thing back and just do it better.","index":66,"end_time":213.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":210.79,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"No worries.","index":67,"end_time":214.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":214.5,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We can walk through it today.","index":68,"end_time":215.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":214.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s perfect timing.","index":69,"end_time":216.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":215.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This is a much easier way of doing it, but obviously I was doing it over a couple of days, so.","index":70,"end_time":221.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":216.98,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, no understandable.","index":71,"end_time":223.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":221.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Well, for Survey Monkey, I''ve seen two new ones come in since we sent that reminder warning.","index":72,"end_time":230.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":225.06,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I''ll keep you updated there.","index":73,"end_time":232.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":230.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And also whenever we do the next one, we''ll switch out the domain so we can hopefully prevent anything from going to the spam folder next time.","index":74,"end_time":240.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":233.14,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But I''ll continue to monitor those new responses and then I''ll give it to the end of the week again on Friday and I''ll send you a new PDF with the current responses that we have and hopefully we have a few more in there and then we''ll just keep looking through it, see what comes up.","index":75,"end_time":254.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":240.18,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But to see a couple new ones come through.","index":76,"end_time":257.089,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":254.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, Isn''t it?","index":77,"end_time":258.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":257.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Because it''s half of what we got last time.","index":78,"end_time":260.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":258.41,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":79,"end_time":262.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":261.57,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And certainly I just see from your list here, so many were opened.","index":80,"end_time":265.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":262.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":81,"end_time":267.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":266.86,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That is crazy.","index":82,"end_time":267.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":267.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I feel like.","index":83,"end_time":268.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":267.98,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, it''s so easy to do, isn''t it?","index":84,"end_time":272.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":270.46,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You think?","index":85,"end_time":272.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":272.1,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I did try.","index":86,"end_time":274.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":274.22,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I did have a quick sort of chat with Josh about maybe, you know, financial incentives.","index":87,"end_time":278.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":274.86,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"He wasn''t keen.","index":88,"end_time":279.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":278.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I didn''t know if we gave him like a ten dollar Starbucks, would that make a difference?","index":89,"end_time":284.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":280.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":90,"end_time":285.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":284.94,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''ve seen people do like enter to win the chance.","index":91,"end_time":290.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":286.94,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So then you just do like one like $50 gift card that goes to one of the responders.","index":92,"end_time":297.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":290.62,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":93,"end_time":299.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":299.23,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay then.","index":94,"end_time":301.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":299.87,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, then you''re not on the line for a lot of money.","index":95,"end_time":304.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":301.11,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You just give away one.","index":96,"end_time":305.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":304.15,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Well, right now I''m not giving away at all.","index":97,"end_time":310.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":306.11,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, it''s probably worth a thought, isn''t it?","index":98,"end_time":312.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":310.75,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I suppose if we wanted to do it again, I mean, I don''t know.","index":99,"end_time":317.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":312.79,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think at the moment the answers are fairly varied.","index":100,"end_time":321.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":317.71,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So that makes me think I haven''t got much in terms of consistency.","index":101,"end_time":325.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":321.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Whereas the first one I had very easy consistency because, you know, the 15 questions, they all answer them in a very similar sort of way.","index":102,"end_time":332.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":325.05,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So, you know, good answers, good number of responses or the for a majority answer.","index":103,"end_time":339.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":332.57,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Did you also send it to your clients, this most recent one?","index":104,"end_time":344.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":340.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":105,"end_time":346.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":345.82,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We, we normally had that through HubSpot, didn''t we?","index":106,"end_time":351.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":347.74,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, that distribution list was through HubSpot.","index":107,"end_time":354.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":351.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''re going to link.","index":108,"end_time":356.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":354.62,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Link to the new survey through the new newsletter we''re about to publish, which will go out through HubSpot to the clients and then also the additional list in mailchimp so that that other link may help us get more additional ones.","index":109,"end_time":369.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":356.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So it''s an external link, Bailey.","index":110,"end_time":372.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":369.78,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s not through SurveyMonkey, so that way people can click it, but it still goes through SurveyMonkey.","index":111,"end_time":376.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":372.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I''m hoping that that''ll get more people like their clients and other.","index":112,"end_time":379.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":376.69,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Other audiences like that to help.","index":113,"end_time":381.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":379.93,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Good point.","index":114,"end_time":383.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":382.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I did forget about that one.","index":115,"end_time":384.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":383.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, cool.","index":116,"end_time":384.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":384.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yes.","index":117,"end_time":385.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":384.93,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"All right, that''s good.","index":118,"end_time":386.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":385.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s good to see that we see some.","index":119,"end_time":389.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":388.33,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Oh, we get some stats here about open and unopened because obviously we never got those before.","index":120,"end_time":395.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":389.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So it''s nice to see.","index":121,"end_time":396.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":395.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Nice to see that before it was a bit of a black hole, wasn''t it?","index":122,"end_time":401.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":397.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Oh, God knows what happened to them.","index":123,"end_time":403.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":401.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"SurveyMonkey does provide a lot of stats again, a couple.","index":124,"end_time":407.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":403.59,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"A couple of different new ones here that were included.","index":125,"end_time":410.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":407.75,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But yeah, it is interesting to see.","index":126,"end_time":412.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":410.59,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"He may have gone to spam too, like I said, so.","index":127,"end_time":415.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":413.11,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":128,"end_time":416.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":415.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Well, it was good as well to see, you know, who actually responded.","index":129,"end_time":423.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":416.43,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I like that.","index":130,"end_time":424.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":423.91,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That was.","index":131,"end_time":424.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":424.55,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That was.","index":132,"end_time":425.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":424.91,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That is a cool feature for sure.","index":133,"end_time":427.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":425.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, it is nice.","index":134,"end_time":429.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":427.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I do like that.","index":135,"end_time":430.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":429.72,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":136,"end_time":430.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":430.48,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Now that is awesome.","index":137,"end_time":433.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":432.68,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Cool.","index":138,"end_time":434.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":433.96,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"All right, great.","index":139,"end_time":435.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":434.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Lovely to see.","index":140,"end_time":436.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":435.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So then as we were just talking about that newsletter, I''ll go ahead and.","index":141,"end_time":439.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":437,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I already started sending it to the design team with the current edits that you had sent back.","index":142,"end_time":444.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":440.04,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we''ll just reformat a couple of things.","index":143,"end_time":446.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":444.28,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I had already made a note to that light bulb and that long bar.","index":144,"end_time":449.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":446.28,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think it could just be reformatted so we kind of reduce that white space like you were talking about.","index":145,"end_time":454.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":449.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That was the only.","index":146,"end_time":455.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":455.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like I say, it was the only thing it suddenly it felt like there was so much empty space and the letters were very small and I had to make it bigger.","index":147,"end_time":462.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":455.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, those should be quick fixes that we.","index":148,"end_time":466.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":464.47,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, it''s just.","index":149,"end_time":467.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":466.43,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s just so sort of.","index":150,"end_time":468.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":467.27,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Anyone can read it.","index":151,"end_time":469.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":468.19,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They don''t want to sort of be squinting and getting close to the screen.","index":152,"end_time":472.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":469.07,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Exactly.","index":153,"end_time":473.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":472.79,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Want to make it as easy as possible.","index":154,"end_time":474.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":473.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I do like the bar they created though, with the.","index":155,"end_time":477.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":475.11,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"The survey links.","index":156,"end_time":478.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":477.91,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That way hopefully it stands out a little bit more so people can.","index":157,"end_time":481.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":478.75,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Can click that with the color behind it.","index":158,"end_time":483.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":481.56,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":159,"end_time":484.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":483.64,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And yeah, good, good idea to use the green space for phase two.","index":160,"end_time":488.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":484.28,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That was.","index":161,"end_time":489.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":488.6,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That was a really clever idea.","index":162,"end_time":490.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":489.04,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I like that.","index":163,"end_time":491.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":490.52,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yes.","index":164,"end_time":491.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":491.08,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Wanted to keep it similar to the newsletter we normally have, but also kind of make it a little differentiated from the typical things that we put out, since it does include the survey results.","index":165,"end_time":500.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":491.48,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So that way we can use it again in the future whenever we do.","index":166,"end_time":503.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":500.6,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"If you do another survey and do the results again.","index":167,"end_time":505.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":503.72,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, utilize that again.","index":168,"end_time":507.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":506.12,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Great.","index":169,"end_time":508.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":508.5,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So the booth and brochure will have our teamwork on that final file for print now that that is confirmed.","index":170,"end_time":515.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":509.86,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yep.","index":171,"end_time":516.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":515.94,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then I just had this on here until you went ahead and sent this.","index":172,"end_time":520.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":517.06,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I''ll go ahead and put this.","index":173,"end_time":523.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":520.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Here so you can read the notes.","index":174,"end_time":526.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":523.46,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Can you see the.","index":175,"end_time":526.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":526.1,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Can you read the comments on this?","index":176,"end_time":528.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":526.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I wonder if I have to open it through Google Docs.","index":177,"end_time":531.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":529.3,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Let me see.","index":178,"end_time":532.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":531.82,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Doesn''t work at all.","index":179,"end_time":535.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":533.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I can just send it to you in a different way.","index":180,"end_time":537.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":535.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It looks like it''s not letting me open your comments.","index":181,"end_time":543.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":541.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"No worries.","index":182,"end_time":544.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":544.28,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''ll.","index":183,"end_time":545.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":544.92,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''ll send you the comments then.","index":184,"end_time":547.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":545.64,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay, I''ll send you the comments.","index":185,"end_time":549,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":547.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s fine.","index":186,"end_time":549.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":549.24,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So here''s.","index":187,"end_time":551.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":549.96,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Here''s the thinking when I was looking through the brochure, and I apologize, I have to say, I stared at it for some time, and then I was looking at the old one, and I''m staring at it again and going, something''s not right.","index":188,"end_time":562.76,"speaker_id":