"speaker_id":2,"start_time":603.44,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s a little bit easier to read quickly is what my thinking was, because I was trying to visualize someone walking past.","index":203,"end_time":612.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":605.2,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They look at the booth, they get hopefully some good insights and that then they look at this and they go, should I scan this?","index":204,"end_time":619.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":612.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I was thinking, give you the reason to scan it.","index":205,"end_time":622.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":619.86,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And that''s the.","index":206,"end_time":623.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":622.66,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''s why I thought shorter text would be.","index":207,"end_time":625.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":623.38,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But I''ll resend that to you separately.","index":208,"end_time":628.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":625.58,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, that sounds good.","index":209,"end_time":629.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":628.66,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I know we had talked about that last week, how we don''t want it to be about these two.","index":210,"end_time":632.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":629.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What''s in these QR codes because we want them to scan them and figure it out.","index":211,"end_time":636.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":633.22,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So it wanted more an overview of Hydra.","index":212,"end_time":638.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":636.46,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so.","index":213,"end_time":639.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":638.62,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, that.","index":214,"end_time":639.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":639.22,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That makes sense.","index":215,"end_time":640.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":639.82,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then I 