m is four.","index":277,"end_time":785.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":784.04,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I couldn''t.","index":278,"end_time":787.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":786.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I could not think of a different way of writing this.","index":279,"end_time":789.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":787.44,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I think.","index":280,"end_time":791,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":790.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Because the last one, when it said, grow your team, and that made absolutely no sense to me at all.","index":281,"end_time":795.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":791,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So.","index":282,"end_time":796.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":795.92,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And that is historic.","index":283,"end_time":797.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":796.24,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So it''s not you guys.","index":284,"end_time":798.199,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":797.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s.","index":285,"end_time":798.439,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":798.199,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s what Hydra wrote before.","index":286,"end_time":800.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":798.439,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I just thought this was better in terms of the messaging that I think we are giving.","index":287,"end_time":806.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":800.96,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Giving our clients.","index":288,"end_time":808.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":807.12,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I mean, honestly, guys, we are doing so much more advisory.","index":289,"end_time":814.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":809.97,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"People are asking us to now do far more in terms of how should we change?","index":290,"end_time":820.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":816.53,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What processes should we change?","index":291,"end_time":822.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":821.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How should we.","index":292,"end_time":823.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":823.01,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How should this individual actually do this particular task?","index":293,"end_time":827.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":823.69,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''re getting all that we''re doing.","index":294,"end_time":828.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":827.17,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You know, Josh is going, we''re a software company.","index":295,"end_time":831.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":829.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They don''t think that way.","index":296,"end_time":833.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":831.97,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think very, very differently.","index":297,"end_time":834.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":833.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They look at it.","index":298,"end_time":835.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":834.57,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They go, we love your technology because it gives us the answers, but what we really want is you to tell us, what do we do now?","index":299,"end_time":841.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":835.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How do we do this?","index":300,"end_time":842.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":841.85,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So it''s interesting.","index":301,"end_time":845.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":844.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So how.","index":302,"end_time":845.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":845.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How we''re all trying to move it, and I think I''m trying to feed that sort of information back into this.","index":303,"end_time":851.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":845.73,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So, like I say, you guys did a brilliant job, but again, it''s a little bit of a moving target because, you know, we are having to adapt the way we take work on now.","index":304,"end_time":862.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":851.05,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And because we''re not a software in a box that does one thing, you know, we have that flexibility.","index":305,"end_time":869.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":862.89,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"People are starting to go, well, that''s great.","index":306,"end_time":871.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":869.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Well, now you could do this.","index":307,"end_time":872.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":871.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Could you also do that?","index":308,"end_time":873.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":872.05,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And.","index":309,"end_time":873.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":873.17,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And we evolve the systems or the technology.","index":310,"end_time":876.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":873.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We would say technology.","index":311,"end_time":879.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":878.33,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s not.","index":312,"end_time":879.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":879.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We basically, you know, write new.","index":313,"end_time":881.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":879.69,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"New programs that spit out different things, you know, or we use different AI tools to give us different things.","index":314,"end_time":889.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":882.01,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So it''s still the same technology in terms of.","index":315,"end_time":892.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":889.97,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s, you know, it''s writing code to then spit out, you know, a better outcome.","index":316,"end_time":898.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":893.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So that''s.","index":317,"end_time":900.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":899.81,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''s why I''m a little bit.","index":318,"end_time":901.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":900.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''re not producing anything else.","index":319,"end_time":902.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":901.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You know, that.","index":320,"end_time":903.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":902.81,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That is not bespoke.","index":321,"end_time":906.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":903.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Anyway, I''m going off on a tangent, but my point is, is I''m trying to make this a little bit more advisory, a little bit more results orientated.","index":322,"end_time":917.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":907.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s not software, but it''s not consulting.","index":323,"end_time":919.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":917.07,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''re still falling into the same sort of trap of.","index":324,"end_time":923.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":920.03,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s a.","index":325,"end_time":923.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":923.27,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s a hybrid of the two, you know, and I''m trying to make sure that people read it.","index":326,"end_time":928.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":923.67,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And what I want them to do is read it and go, yeah, that makes perfect sense.","index":327,"end_time":931.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":928.71,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I understand why I''m coming to you.","index":328,"end_time":933.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":931.99,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, that makes A lot of sense, too, because like you said, you''re going to use it for these trade shows, too, and handing them out to people, so making sure it''s a little aligned with what they''re going to go see on your website.","index":329,"end_time":944.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":935.95,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But also the things that scan the QR code and go to see those additional assets that we''ve worked on too.","index":330,"end_time":950.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":944.74,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And.","index":331,"end_time":950.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":950.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But only that.","index":332,"end_time":951.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":950.98,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But also when they start having a conversation with us and we start.","index":333,"end_time":953.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":951.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We have to be consistent in our messaging, because if they get on the phone and they go, I think you''re this.","index":334,"end_time":959.419,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":954.14,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then we go down a different path, and that''s going to confuse everyone.","index":335,"end_time":963.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":959.42,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I''m trying my hardest to get this right.","index":336,"end_time":965.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":963.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Quick question on that.","index":337,"end_time":968.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":967.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How do you think your clients would refer to you?","index":338,"end_time":971.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":968.26,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like, if they were like, who''s Hydrien?","index":339,"end_time":974.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":972.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What do you think they would say?","index":340,"end_time":975.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":974.46,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, I. I agree.","index":341,"end_time":978.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":977.78,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I mean, I would say if we looked at the testimonials from the two or three that have done ones with us, it''s all been the same sorts of things.","index":342,"end_time":987.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":978.82,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They come in, they understand the problem and they give us answers and they tell us what to do.","index":343,"end_time":993.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":987.1,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You know, no one says.","index":344,"end_time":995.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":993.94,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They got this really, really clever bit of software that just.","index":345,"end_time":998.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":995.87,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They don''t say any of that.","index":346,"end_time":1000.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":998.63,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They literally say, come in, understand the problem, find out how to solve it, and tell us what to do.","index":347,"end_time":1007.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1000.75,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Do you think you have any current clients that would maybe be open to doing more testimonials?","index":348,"end_time":1013.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1008.51,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like, even just like, something over zoom?","index":349,"end_time":1015.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1013.95,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We did talk about that today with one of them, Imperial.","index":350,"end_time":1020.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1016.67,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"The only thing we might have to.","index":351,"end_time":1022.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1021.48,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We might.","index":352,"end_time":1022.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1022.6,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''re a little bit concerned about Imperial.","index":353,"end_time":1024.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1022.92,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They''re a distributor for like.","index":354,"end_time":1026.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1025.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like truck parts, but they''re part.","index":355,"end_time":1030.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1028.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They''re part of Granger, and Granger doesn''t want to know that.","index":356,"end_time":1035.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1030.68,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They do their own thing.","index":357,"end_time":1036.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1035.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we don''t know if we''re going to get permission.","index":358,"end_time":1038.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1036.48,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But yes, Bailey is.","index":359,"end_time":1040.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1038.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We.","index":360,"end_time":1040.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1040.64,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We desperately should get a couple more testimonials, even if it is, like, you say, over zoom and we just.","index":361,"end_time":1048.169,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1040.92,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, just something anonymous, too.","index":362,"end_time":1050.449,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1048.169,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, we could do that.","index":363,"end_time":1052.449,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1051.409,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I mean, they''re open.","index":364,"end_time":1054.369,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1052.449,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, we could do that.","index":365,"end_time":1056.329,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1055.409,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I could suggest that to Josh.","index":366,"end_time":1057.809,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1056.329,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, let me make a note of that before I forget, because I''m chatting with him tomorrow.","index":367,"end_time":1061.809,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1057.889,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, that''s something.","index":368,"end_time":1063.489,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1062.609,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I know Taylor''s done quite a few of those, too.","index":369,"end_time":1065.809,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1063.489,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like, sometimes it''s good to have a third party come in and do the interview because it''s maybe a little less pressure.","index":370,"end_time":1071.489,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1065.809,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You''re talking to someone different.","index":371,"end_time":1073.569,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1072.049,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So, like, if you wanted to allocate some points to that.","index":372,"end_time":1077.009,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1073.969,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''d be happy to help there, or if you want to do that too.","index":373,"end_time":1081.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1078.12,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Whatever.","index":374,"end_time":1081.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1081.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Whatever works.","index":375,"end_time":1083,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1082.04,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But yeah, those case studies and testimonials are like, a really big part of the, the buying journey.","index":376,"end_time":1092.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1085.96,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Oh, yeah, I agree.","index":377,"end_time":1094.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1093.24,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I agree.","index":378,"end_time":1097.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1096.92,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":379,"end_time":1098.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1097.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":380,"end_time":1098.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1098.24,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I made a note of that.","index":381,"end_time":1099.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1098.52,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''ll have that conversation with him tomorrow, and then I''ll come back and let you know.","index":382,"end_time":1103.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1099.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Awesome.","index":383,"end_time":1104.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1104.18,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Great.","index":384,"end_time":1105.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1105.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Those can be turned into great pieces of content too, for the website and stuff like that that we can add in, so.","index":385,"end_time":1112.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1107.14,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Totally.","index":386,"end_time":1112.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1112.1,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":387,"end_time":1112.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1112.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I mean, like I say, I think we need more anyway.","index":388,"end_time":1116.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1112.98,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We do need more case studies and stories and things like that.","index":389,"end_time":1119.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1116.5,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like I say, you and I, Taylor, we''ve talked about this quite a few times.","index":390,"end_time":1123.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1119.62,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You know, having, you know, what have we learned?","index":391,"end_time":1125.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1123.06,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What''s the latest, you know, what can we share?","index":392,"end_time":1127.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1125.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Love to do all those sorts of things.","index":393,"end_time":1130.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1129.55,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I really would.","index":394,"end_time":1131.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1130.71,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yes.","index":395,"end_time":1131.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1131.39,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":396,"end_time":1133.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1132.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And again, I think we can still make it anonymous.","index":397,"end_time":1135.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1133.19,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"If we can''t name names, we can certainly make, you know, we work for so and so.","index":398,"end_time":1140.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1135.39,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And this is what we did.","index":399,"end_time":1141.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1140.03,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This is their problem.","index":400,"end_time":1141.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1141.19,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This is how we achieved it.","index":401,"end_time":1143.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1141.95,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That case study sort of thing.","index":402,"end_time":1144.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1143.39,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Exactly.","index":403,"end_time":1147.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1146.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":404,"end_time":1147.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1147.55,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":405,"end_time":1148.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1147.99,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Great.","index":406,"end_time":1150.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1150.03,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Perfect.","index":407,"end_time":1152.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1151.79,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So, like I said, we''ll work on that final design for the booth, and I''ll send that over to you as soon as we have that ready.","index":408,"end_time":1158.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1152.67,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Did you, I, I.","index":409,"end_time":1160.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1159.57,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Sorry to interrupt you.","index":410,"end_time":1161.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1160.93,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I, I attached this the, the files template.","index":411,"end_time":1165.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1161.93,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":412,"end_time":1165.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1165.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":413,"end_time":1165.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1165.53,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Just want to make sure that came across.","index":414,"end_time":1167.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1165.89,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yes, that''s the most important part.","index":415,"end_time":1169.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1167.41,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I made sure to include that to our designers so we can have it all ready.","index":416,"end_time":1172.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1169.17,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Absolutely.","index":417,"end_time":1172.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1172.41,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Cool.","index":418,"end_time":1173.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1173.01,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"All right.","index":419,"end_time":1173.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1173.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":420,"end_time":1175.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1174.69,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so then just the last minute additional updates here.","index":421,"end_time":1177.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1175.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"The carousel post you and I had talked about last week too.","index":422,"end_time":1179.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1177.53,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''re just finalizing that copy outline that I wanted to share with you, so I''ll send that over most likely later today so you can see kind of how that flow.","index":423,"end_time":1186.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1179.97,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then if you want to make any ad assessments about what the wording specifically would look like, because I know we.","index":424,"end_time":1191.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1186.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We pulled from the specific copies that you gave us for those four post structure, but if you want to change anything, I''ll just open it for an open edit access and then we can build the designs from there, so.","index":425,"end_time":1203.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1191.87,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Lovely.","index":426,"end_time":1203.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1203.03,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, I''m excited about that, actually, because I showed it to Josh and we used that example, and I think it''s interesting.","index":427,"end_time":1208.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1203.47,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, it''d be interesting to sort of see what we can do with it.","index":428,"end_time":1211.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1208.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, I think it''ll look really cool.","index":429,"end_time":1213.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1211.55,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And two, if you have a cool testimonial that we end up doing.","index":430,"end_time":1215.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1213.64,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We can end up doing a carousel too, for that, where you can advertise that on socials to love it.","index":431,"end_time":1221.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1215.96,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Get your message across too, about what you do on there as well.","index":432,"end_time":1225.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1221.64,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So, yeah, we can.","index":433,"end_time":1227.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1225.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, we definitely need to do that.","index":434,"end_time":1228.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1227.08,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":435,"end_time":1229.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1228.68,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Cool.","index":436,"end_time":1229.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1229.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then I know next week we''ll meet for an hour and we''ll go through brainstorming sessions that.","index":437,"end_time":1235,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1230.2,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"With all these topics and we''ll also make sure to review that strategy and goals session document two that you gave us.","index":438,"end_time":1241.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1235.16,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So, yeah, have a read through that because I think I''m hoping that''s going to be useful because that''s, that''s our thinking, what we think we should do with it.","index":439,"end_time":1250.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1241.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You know, still a bit of a work in progress because I''m sure I''m learning as I go along.","index":440,"end_time":1255.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1250.01,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like I said, the referral partnership thing, I have no idea how that works.","index":441,"end_time":1259.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1255.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''m just trying to think about whether it is going to be, you know, a good approach.","index":442,"end_time":1264.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1259.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So, yeah, thoughts on all of it would be great.","index":443,"end_time":1268.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1264.73,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Awesome.","index":444,"end_time":1269.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1269.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That sounds good.","index":445,"end_time":1270.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1269.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Well, we''re looking forward to it.","index":446,"end_time":1271.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1270.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''ll be a good discussion and I''m glad we have a little bit longer time to get through everything too.","index":447,"end_time":1276.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1272.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So.","index":448,"end_time":1277.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1276.81,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, absolutely.","index":449,"end_time":1278.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1277.93,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I did sell Josh.","index":450,"end_time":1279.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1278.73,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"He has to be on that one.","index":451,"end_time":1281.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1279.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Let him know.","index":452,"end_time":1283.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1282.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, do not miss that one.","index":453,"end_time":1286.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1283.85,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Perfect.","index":454,"end_time":1287.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1287.37,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That sounds good.","index":455,"end_time":1288.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1288.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''ll keep you updated through email with all the other updates that we just mentioned.","index":456,"end_time":1292.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1288.97,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And yeah, be on the lookout for anything new from you as well.","index":457,"end_time":1296.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1292.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yep.","index":458,"end_time":1296.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1296.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''ll.","index":459,"end_time":1296.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1296.57,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''ll go back and I will take those two pages that you can''t see the.","index":460,"end_time":1302.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1296.89,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"The stuff.","index":461,"end_time":1303.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1303.17,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I''ll try, I''ll try to make it.","index":462,"end_time":1305.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1303.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I was going to go ahead and photograph photocopy, like all my pieces of paper that I wrote on.","index":463,"end_time":1312.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1306.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I didn''t think.","index":464,"end_time":1313.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1312.53,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I will send that to you and hopefully it all makes sense.","index":465,"end_time":1318.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1316.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It doesn''t just jump on the phone and we can go through it.","index":466,"end_time":1321.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1318.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":467,"end_time":1322.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1321.52,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That sounds good.","index":468,"end_time":1322.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1322.28,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Thank you.","index":469,"end_time":1323.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1322.96,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Michael.","index":470,"end_time":1323.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1323.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Would it.","index":471,"end_time":1324.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1323.68,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Would it be easier.","index":472,"end_time":1325.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1324.12,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''m just thinking.","index":473,"end_time":1325.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1325.04,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I just thought if I send it to you in a markup link so you can add your comments that way.","index":474,"end_time":1330.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1325.72,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Or would you rather.","index":475,"end_time":1330.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1330.08,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Well, of course.","index":476,"end_time":1332.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1331.28,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":477,"end_time":1333.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1332.48,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I was just thinking, I was like, there''s got to be an easier way to do this.","index":478,"end_time":1336.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1333.2,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''m like, I can send it to you through markup.","index":479,"end_time":1338.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1336.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I''ll just put all those designs and markups so you can do it that way.","index":480,"end_time":1340.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1338.04,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":481,"end_time":1341.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1340.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Think of something simple for the old people.","index":482,"end_time":1343.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1341.44,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Come on.","index":483,"end_time":1343.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1343.2,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You know, honestly, I prefer it too.","index":484,"end_time":1346.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1343.68,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It can be complicated when you have a lot of feedback.","index":485,"end_time":1348.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1346.64,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I''ll send it to you in markup that you could go from there.","index":486,"end_time":1351.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1348.72,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Lovely.","index":487,"end_time":1352.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1351.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I appreciate that.","index":488,"end_time":1352.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1352.22,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Be much easier then.","index":489,"end_time":1353.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1352.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Of course, it would be a lot neater as well.","index":490,"end_time":1355.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1353.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, send it to me for all three and I''ll ignore those that I''ve sent and I''ll just transfer them all across into the new one.","index":491,"end_time":1362.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1355.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Perfect.","index":492,"end_time":1363.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1362.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That sounds good.","index":493,"end_time":1364.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1363.18,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''ll do that right after this.","index":494,"end_time":1365.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1364.22,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Fantastic.","index":495,"end_time":1366.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1365.74,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Thank you, guys.","index":496,"end_time":1367.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1366.5,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I appreciate it.","index":497,"end_time":1368.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1367.18,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Looking forward to next week.","index":498,"end_time":1369.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1368.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And, yeah, let''s just.","index":499,"end_time":1371.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1369.98,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''ll just do the strategy thing next week.","index":500,"end_time":1373.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1371.98,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Just make it as you structured how well you think, and then we''ll just, we''ll add our bits.","index":501,"end_tim