on my end for this.","index":48,"end_time":129.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":126.34,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay.","index":49,"end_time":130.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":130.42,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So you''re.","index":50,"end_time":131.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":130.9,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"You ready to go ahead and launch?","index":51,"end_time":132.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":131.34,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yes.","index":52,"end_time":133.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":132.94,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay.","index":53,"end_time":134.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":133.5,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The only question I had outstanding is this is marked, I think, as an archived comment.","index":54,"end_time":137.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":134.02,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I don''t know if this is still a change you want to see reflected or if biopharma companies is what you want it to say.","index":55,"end_time":144.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":137.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"This was for hospitals and Life Sciences.","index":56,"end_time":147.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":144.26,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay, I will update that.","index":57,"end_time":148.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":147.34,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Then we''ll make sure that is reflected.","index":58,"end_time":150.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":148.7,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, I think Life Sciences encompasses biopharma to the extent it needs to and is more targeted at the tissue digestor and effluent decon side of things.","index":59,"end_time":162.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":150.62,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay.","index":60,"end_time":163.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":162.71,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So certainly for this homepage, I Think we want it to be hospitals and life sciences.","index":61,"end_time":167.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":163.51,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay.","index":62,"end_time":168.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":168.31,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yep, we will update that.","index":63,"end_time":170.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":168.79,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Great.","index":64,"end_time":171.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":171.43,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Well, that''s exciting.","index":65,"end_time":172.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":171.79,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I will let our developer know.","index":66,"end_time":174.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":173.11,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I had him on standby this morning.","index":67,"end_time":176.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":174.75,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We just wanted to confirm on your end that everything looked good.","index":68,"end_time":179.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":176.91,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I did want to talk.","index":69,"end_time":182.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":180.95,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We''ll go ahead and launch this now, make sure everything''s good to go, depending on what he had to do.","index":70,"end_time":187.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":182.19,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"He did mention to me that he wants to make sure all of the latest blogs and articles we''ve uploaded are also implemented before launch.","index":71,"end_time":194.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":187.51,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So he may have to work on that.","index":72,"end_time":195.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":194.43,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And we''d launch early tomorrow morning just so we can monitor it throughout the day.","index":73,"end_time":199.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":195.59,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But we''ll go ahead and do that.","index":74,"end_time":201.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":199.79,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But for that additional page that you had emailed me about the available inventory, I know you had mentioned it''s going to live between these two here.","index":75,"end_time":210.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":202.27,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then I was going through the requirements.","index":76,"end_time":212.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":210.75,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I just want to make sure we build out the page correctly.","index":77,"end_time":214.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":212.39,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Um, it''s going to have space for any given piece of inventory.","index":78,"end_time":218.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":215.13,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So when we build out the design, do you want us to have.","index":79,"end_time":221.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":218.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Are they going to be, like, blank sections, or do you want us to have something specifically listed on this site when we build the design out and.","index":80,"end_time":229.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":221.85,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"As well as, like, these paragraphs and everything like that?","index":81,"end_time":231.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":229.57,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Will you provide that, or is there somewhere you''d like us to look?","index":82,"end_time":234.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":231.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I. I will pro.","index":83,"end_time":235.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":234.57,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I will provide that.","index":84,"end_time":236.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":235.73,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I think I want to be.","index":85,"end_time":237.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":236.73,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I want it to be set up so that there''s a common template for any of these pieces so that we''re able to get.","index":86,"end_time":246.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":237.93,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Get them up and take them off quickly and easily.","index":87,"end_time":249.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":246.86,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay.","index":88,"end_time":250.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":249.98,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"You know, and most of them will probably be, you know, variants of each other, you know, pretty similar, but we may have kind of random stuff in that I want to just make sure we can.","index":89,"end_time":264.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":251.26,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Put up in the.","index":90,"end_time":269.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":268.71,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"In the format without it breaking anything.","index":91,"end_time":271.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":269.35,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"And I.","index":92,"end_time":272.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":271.51,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So I think what that looks like is having, like, a title, like a sub line, some pictures, and then space, like for a paragraph of text.","index":93,"end_time":280.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":272.07,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Right.","index":94,"end_time":281.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":281.51,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, it makes sense.","index":95,"end_time":283.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":282.07,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":96,"end_time":284.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":284.39,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"And then if we have the ability to kind of attach files into whatever that is, so we could have like a cut sheet, like, you know, O and M manual, whatever else associated with it, that would be awesome.","index":97,"end_time":296.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":284.71,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay, great.","index":98,"end_time":297.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":297.1,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, we''ll look for you for those specifics and we can build out a design like we do.","index":99,"end_time":302.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":297.74,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We have all the designs in here.","index":100,"end_time":305.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":303.66,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I was just looking through that this morning to see if we could get that started.","index":101,"end_time":309.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":305.3,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we''ll accrue from those details and we can build that out to show you.","index":102,"end_time":312.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":309.26,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Cool.","index":103,"end_time":312.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":312.5,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And I''ll get what we have on the floor now that we''d want to have listed up there, and that''ll be what we start off with.","index":104,"end_time":318.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":312.78,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":105,"end_time":319.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":318.94,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That sounds good.","index":106,"end_time":320.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":319.38,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But, yeah, we won''t let that hold up this launch.","index":107,"end_time":323.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":320.78,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I''ll send all this information over.","index":108,"end_time":325.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":323.18,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Was there any other updates as far as the carousel images or GIFs or anything like that that you wanted to review or just.","index":109,"end_time":331.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":325.02,"speaker_name"